{"note_id": "66cd6cf6000000001f038de8", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪大狗屎，拉文克劳饮品大狗屎，奶盖大狗", "desc": "如题，这个芝士葡萄真的感觉很难喝，喝到一半直接全吐了。。。斯莱特林的猕猴桃味特别浓也还好不知道其他院口味如何#奈雪的茶联名哈利波特[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1724738806000, "last_update_time": 1771944176000, "user_id": "5e9e43ba0000000001004e1e", "nickname": "七月无晴天", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31otmcsaohk6g5nku8et08jgugkrd0b8", "liked_count": "624", "collected_count": "35", "comment_count": "685", "share_count": "214", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/ec837a67436a758a2e3e7e6189d8f0f8/1040g2sg31709pe80judg5nku8et08jgu5v3edb8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/0aeb62769ec6f8344899ca702d7a7678/1040g2sg31709pe80jud05nku8et08jguofo8qng!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/6e246a928e71e95492e2aec6d90c665a/1040g2sg31709pe80jucg5nku8et08jgu12rvuio!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶联名哈利波特", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419190, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66cd6cf6000000001f038de8?xsec_token=ABvqv9SBUufYO-QeyW28p4iOWhDCc3u9slHXybwetXCXc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABvqv9SBUufYO-QeyW28p4iOWhDCc3u9slHXybwetXCXc="}
{"note_id": "685917010000000012015239", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪你怎么退步成这样", "desc": "把蓝莓桑葚和酸奶混合一下就算奶茶成品了吗 入口完全感觉不到任何技术含量啊....#奶茶测评[话题]# #果茶爱好者[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1750669057000, "last_update_time": 1750669057000, "user_id": "64d8a5b0000000000200e3ad", "nickname": "今天捡到猫了没", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31u154jja1a005p6okmo0hotdv97av68", "liked_count": "616", "collected_count": "99", "comment_count": "302", "share_count": "82", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/a4967bc86b215d9b000996aa9e5b14e5/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031j2m8iuogs005p6okmo0hotd8jdqcc0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/ecea32e921f2aa85d12cbf0ba55fe186/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031j2m8iuogs0g5p6okmo0hotdov2qaho!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶测评,果茶爱好者", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419190, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/685917010000000012015239?xsec_token=AByQ38EN6nqSqu0Sw7vpzslr_FnFet8kWRYDae5MP-WvU=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AByQ38EN6nqSqu0Sw7vpzslr_FnFet8kWRYDae5MP-WvU="}
{"note_id": "67dbbbe6000000001d01c651", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪这杯真是全方位完蛋", "desc": "名字是叫浓抹，但一点抹茶味都没有，就感觉是有点点青草味的牛奶，点了不另外加糖还是齁甜，珍珠分量有点太喧宾夺主了，喝不到一点茶香，全是甜腻的味道，浓到我自己加了条抹茶粉进去（还兑了水）都没办法稀释一点原本的甜腻感 抹茶、牛奶、珍珠三者之间一点都没有平衡好。\n同类产品中喜茶的水牛乳冻抹茶小料和茶底的平衡就很好，没有过甜也保留了抹茶的味道；茶理宜世的特浓厚抹茶和特浓抹茶与白，虽然是奶盖干酪款，但是抹茶味足够浓且茶汤和奶味平衡的够好，即使加了黑糖珍珠也没有过于甜腻。\n总得来说，奈雪这款给我一种想赶抹茶热度（毕竟几大奶茶品牌就他还没有抹茶类产品了），但没做好研发，匆匆上市的感觉。一点也不像奈雪一贯奶茶出品的品控，反而更像是随便一个普通奶茶店做出来的效果\n#奶茶测评[话题]# #今天喝什么[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #一起嚯奶茶[话题]# #本来就该喝⽔[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪浓抹黑珍珠[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1742453734000, "last_update_time": 1742453734000, "user_id": "5af133ec4eacab7ba5502aa5", "nickname": "PENNIE-", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31q6jgls9n0604a5521puoal5vv6614g", "liked_count": "309", "collected_count": "27", "comment_count": "211", "share_count": "129", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/c8522c6631dad13de1fa44e3b33225fb/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031f88gpcm6q3g4a5521puoal5qnsa0jg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/b1532a8d211b2d8a13c556805f924fdf/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031f88gpcm6q2g4a5521puoal5luqfqmo!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶测评,今天喝什么,奶茶,一起嚯奶茶,本来就该喝⽔,奈雪的茶,奈雪浓抹黑珍珠", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419191, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67dbbbe6000000001d01c651?xsec_token=ABTKlwPgYoOejqmr5jmOOaWco6q822YHwkNASRjRz5zgc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABTKlwPgYoOejqmr5jmOOaWco6q822YHwkNASRjRz5zgc="}
{"note_id": "6912dfb700000000070366f9", "type": "normal", "title": "难如喝", "desc": "水沟油一样，五种东西没一样搭的\n米布味道奇怪，不行呀奈雪新品\n草莓有四分一片吗（照骗[扯脸H]\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪草莓季[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1762844599000, "last_update_time": 1762844599000, "user_id": "59312c996a6a697336918809", "nickname": "vin", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31orgsluuh20049i3f3m9j209ihrkfm0", "liked_count": "302", "collected_count": "26", "comment_count": "228", "share_count": "171", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/c07429a19543471bfc00484d5542c8a9/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031oo3t0kc4q0g49i3f3m9j209e7stt28!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/a04b1761efa98afe7cbe8b8c79f99d63/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031oo3t0kc4q1049i3f3m9j209k2rij5o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,奈雪草莓季", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419191, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6912dfb700000000070366f9?xsec_token=ABpLy-6DJUEGKMJZOepMP-JTNHy6LRQ6Nw5rt3-JeCNqM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABpLy-6DJUEGKMJZOepMP-JTNHy6LRQ6Nw5rt3-JeCNqM="}
{"note_id": "66091ca1000000000401bad3", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶居然不放奶，这还叫奶茶吗？", "desc": "买了三杯同样口味奈雪的奶茶，拿到的时候就有一杯明显颜色很深，当时心想不会没放奶吧？喝了一口后，就是没放奶，很难喝啊！现在的奶茶店做奶茶那么粗糙了吗？连奶都不放了[失望R]#奈雪の茶[话题]# #奈雪奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1711873185000, "last_update_time": 1711873185000, "user_id": "548127a5d6e4a9617b303904", "nickname": "瑟琳娜小姐", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/529594cd91bbf4c43608131bf9134bdc.jpg", "liked_count": "262", "collected_count": "33", "comment_count": "92", "share_count": "7", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/9ab45e8e11f482c824f3630e813bd74d/1040g0083110ivl1dmc00400pl6jqae846n520l0!nd_dft_wgth_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/2d583d85b73b7af13f21d4f40da0e9a2/1040g0083110ivl1dmc0g400pl6jqae846n80g5o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪の茶,奈雪奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419192, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66091ca1000000000401bad3?xsec_token=ABnriFfUO5cRHWgoTllJroM7mgLXe4VlTA4VGIvwVuCYg=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABnriFfUO5cRHWgoTllJroM7mgLXe4VlTA4VGIvwVuCYg="}
{"note_id": "6858c5440000000011000fac", "type": "normal", "title": "终于知道为啥差距那么大了", "desc": "上一条说奈雪酸奶昔的小爆了一下[黄金薯R]有好多人说不稠什么的，今天想喝又喝了一下[喝奶茶R]\n专门点了更远的一家牛油果试了一下[失望R][失望R][失望R]\n结果：难喝！可能是路途原因？快化了，超级稀，以至于奇亚籽的味好重！[泪崩R]\n还是蓝莓的更好喝\n\t\n我觉得还是得近距离刚做出来的真的好好喝，这种带有沙冰🍧感的真的不能放，一个半小时送过来真的成水了！#没有对比就没有伤害[话题]# #不要太离谱[话题]# #奈雪牛油果酸奶昔[话题]# #奈雪酸奶昔[话题]# #奈雪超能牛油果奶昔[话题]# #奈雪66颗蓝莓桑葚酸奶昔[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1750648132000, "last_update_time": 1750648132000, "user_id": "587d82766a6a69231e8896cb", "nickname": "大人类", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31igm75u47q004923tm17d5mb1svfv1g", "liked_count": "238", "collected_count": "21", "comment_count": "106", "share_count": "45", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/8a08d922f527384478cee81b180f823d/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031j2c530sgs004923tm17d5mbevgmhbg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/9da4e4e2fcc835629ebf83a43ff1973c/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031j2c530sgs0g4923tm17d5mb6qv8cho!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "没有对比就没有伤害,不要太离谱,奈雪牛油果酸奶昔,奈雪酸奶昔,奈雪超能牛油果奶昔,奈雪66颗蓝莓桑葚酸奶昔", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419193, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6858c5440000000011000fac?xsec_token=ABBYccMVStSvhcl5CfQrHDGjbE8r5RoRDFRtuVyP7-kfs=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABBYccMVStSvhcl5CfQrHDGjbE8r5RoRDFRtuVyP7-kfs="}
{"note_id": "67dd0284000000001c009b64", "type": "normal", "title": "喜欢苦抹的可以散会了", "desc": "网图看着很浓郁的抹茶，奔现之后我破防了\n点的少冰少少糖，拿到第一口就品了\n很淡的抹茶味💔\n好在奈雪家的黑糖珍珠还是很能打的，牛乳味很香\n#奈雪浓抹黑珍珠[话题]# #奈雪春日来信[话题]#  #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶新品[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1742537348000, "last_update_time": 1742537349000, "user_id": "5ca6f7f30000000010006ef7", "nickname": "Miss.x", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31nstlos5l0005n56uvpk0rnnm8c8nc0", "liked_count": "229", "collected_count": "8", "comment_count": "90", "share_count": "31", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/c4341c6d04354c84a40e2bd24cf94be9/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831f9gg3pils9g5n56uvpk0rnndpbonh8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/b1ad24e9b7e53204470c68e3bc40d728/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831f9gg3pils8g5n56uvpk0rnnqp1vot0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/cc755998089dd204f7dc9db5ea2c67c1/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831f9gg3pilsa05n56uvpk0rnns6k57ng!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪浓抹黑珍珠,奈雪春日来信,奈雪的茶,奈雪的茶新品", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419194, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67dd0284000000001c009b64?xsec_token=ABDGAi-80xkMKS75FhAcXlRoEFl4d4DE-Virq4b2GZjYk=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABDGAi-80xkMKS75FhAcXlRoEFl4d4DE-Virq4b2GZjYk="}
{"note_id": "6507cef8000000001303ee4f", "type": "video", "title": "周杰伦联名的奶茶，他自己都不喝！", "desc": "#内容过于真实[话题]# #奶茶分享[话题]# #搞笑[话题]# #周杰伦[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]##奶茶测评[话题]# #难喝[话题]# #避坑[话题]#", "video_url": "http://sns-video-hs.xhscdn.com/stream/110/259/01e507ceda12428d010371038aa6830dae_259.mp4?sign=289577fb4f1628accdd8999b8a66e5b5&t=69d36001", "time": 1695010552000, "last_update_time": 1695010553000, "user_id": "5d707de50000000001004944", "nickname": "阿紫阿阳", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo315qla88j0s1g5otqlch9gsrk8o80hl8", "liked_count": "134", "collected_count": "16", "comment_count": "66", "share_count": "16", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/27a363963110e1ef07dcf4ab376031c0/1040g00830p5a89v83u005nbgfnig8ia49vitdng!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "内容过于真实,奶茶分享,搞笑,周杰伦,奈雪的茶,奶茶测评,难喝,避坑", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419194, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6507cef8000000001303ee4f?xsec_token=ABsqH7advFhYeOYEMXlXMXOEGUaBaVXf0WYmlSUVZr38k=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABsqH7advFhYeOYEMXlXMXOEGUaBaVXf0WYmlSUVZr38k="}
{"note_id": "66ee56dd0000000012013715", "type": "normal", "title": "被大家嫌弃是有原因的", "desc": "奈雪，可以麻烦借鉴一下别人的配方再做饮品吗\n杨枝甘露最近喝了好几次都是一股水味\n喝完下层的椰汁跟芒果果肉之后完全没味道\n上面一层比兑了水的芒果汁还要稀[再见R]\n这已经是很容易流水线制作的饮品了还如此不堪入口[生气R]真的很失望\n#奈雪[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #杨枝甘露[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1726895837000, "last_update_time": 1726895837000, "user_id": "6021f548000000000100974e", "nickname": "柴柴天使👼", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31709svoago005o11ul4095qea6qpm30", "liked_count": "107", "collected_count": "11", "comment_count": "73", "share_count": "14", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061525/4aaf89bb6c5e96abf63449f09cff9cb1/1040g0083180eb4cigq005o11ul4095qepnj5m50!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪,奈雪的茶,杨枝甘露", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419195, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66ee56dd0000000012013715?xsec_token=ABY5l6sWPVN-nUn9IouAh6Xu_IeuSZTOtwHISmxytrttY=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABY5l6sWPVN-nUn9IouAh6Xu_IeuSZTOtwHISmxytrttY="}
{"note_id": "660f8f8e000000001b00ba1c", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪，你是要谋杀我么？", "desc": "昨天下午三点左右喝的奶茶，一夜没睡，失眠到天明！！终于天亮了，妈蛋，六点了！！！\n感觉灵魂要出窍，身体被掏空了一样，晕乎乎！平时喝花茶，绿茶，红茶，其他品牌奶茶都不会这么严重！！\n就说说，还有谁比我难！", "video_url": "", "time": 1712295822000, "last_update_time": 1712296218000, "user_id": "60e9bec3000000002002df06", "nickname": "玉米粒", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo3133tsbvvi66g5o79nr1o5no6b0507d0", "liked_count": "106", "collected_count": "23", "comment_count": "309", "share_count": "104", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/f823f90454100ac49dc0825d90286f6f/1040g2sg3116sgj6e6i405o79nr1o5no6o0bt0dg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419195, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/660f8f8e000000001b00ba1c?xsec_token=ABpLKqs4ZH8e7GRnoflas2srzMUEuaE1IBWq66PJ9XrAw=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABpLKqs4ZH8e7GRnoflas2srzMUEuaE1IBWq66PJ9XrAw="}
{"note_id": "680f56ec000000002301e8ac", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪，你的研发也加班加疯了吗…", "desc": "每喝一口都是我对24元人民币的尊重\n赞妮这个真的…还蛮难喝的。。。\n第一口喝的时候没有搅，热的桑葚混着稀的酸奶还有果冻，我不知道怎么形容反正挺炸裂的。。。主包喝了一口以后给同伴也喝了一口，两个人都是痛苦面具Orz\n后面搅了一下，只能说不难喝 , 但是花钱单纯为了喝这个饮品没必要。。。。\n还有一个槽点就是我买毛绒套餐默认是大杯，简直是“趁我病要我命”…主包研究了半天发现多的四块原来是因为默认大杯，默默改成了中杯🥲还好买的是中杯，不然我能从早上喝到晚上。。。。\n#鸣潮[话题]# #鸣潮创作激励[话题]# #奈雪鸣潮联动[话题]# #来财[话题]# #鸣潮赞妮[话题]# #难喝[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1745835756000, "last_update_time": 1745835756000, "user_id": "5d1f44df0000000011024468", "nickname": "是恐龙啊", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/6120ff09b2f6d14ef6d4a741.jpg", "liked_count": "97", "collected_count": "2", "comment_count": "58", "share_count": "7", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/ceb9db3a4cfc85cfd13b3869e23a7dc7/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031gqljaut426g5n8v8jfkch3897ii680!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/33dc997238539b5277bca2cb1a57bf32/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031gqljauu3a6g5n8v8jfkch38vj4la18!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/a5f595c305a0f21e024872e67c274e13/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031gqljb09jc6g5n8v8jfkch38qheh09o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/6b00fd28410724868a2165b2893f45a5/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031gqljavg3c605n8v8jfkch38tbqepg8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "鸣潮,鸣潮创作激励,奈雪鸣潮联动,来财,鸣潮赞妮,难喝", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419196, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/680f56ec000000002301e8ac?xsec_token=ABv2ubNptNk4201bq3eVvniMa-DnUY5MKZ_xYG4xTlkz8=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABv2ubNptNk4201bq3eVvniMa-DnUY5MKZ_xYG4xTlkz8="}
{"note_id": "67b13e30000000001800694b", "type": "normal", "title": "人生建议！别喝奈雪的茶！茶！！！", "desc": "昨天下午买了一杯奈雪的茶 茉莉初雪奶茶！！晚上回家就心慌恶心，还失眠！！！晚上12点难受的直接吐了，谁能想到喝杯奶茶也能吐！！现在还不舒服😭#茉莉初雪奶茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #失眠[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1739669040000, "last_update_time": 1739669040000, "user_id": "5c06181644363b29474298a0", "nickname": "噜噜噜", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/669c4bdab8315cc22c1b7c1b.jpg", "liked_count": "87", "collected_count": "23", "comment_count": "196", "share_count": "51", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/b2c0df19a26df85e647957c6db61619a/1040g2sg31dup2nt30s704buqiec1d650ccl9i7o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "茉莉初雪奶茶,奈雪的茶,失眠", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419197, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67b13e30000000001800694b?xsec_token=ABaspuwpSB69Fh1VSNKn-8Bv0j2NM5qQE7eP4KW2xXGf0=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABaspuwpSB69Fh1VSNKn-8Bv0j2NM5qQE7eP4KW2xXGf0="}
{"note_id": "6953da6e000000001e010145", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的霸气芝士草莓改配方了，难喝得钥匙", "desc": "[泪崩R]看到霸气芝士草莓回归了立马点了一杯，结果一口喝下去难喝得钥匙，甜得喉咙齁住了，赶紧吐掉用水漱口。\n\t\n超甜的草莓水加上草莓奶盖，喝起来像呕吐物[完啦R]，不信邪搅匀了再喝了两口，甜得我上蹿下跳。\n\t\n打电话问店员是不是放错糖了，结果告诉我改配方了，查了一下好像从纯草莓变成了加树莓，难喝难喝！！！\n#奈雪[话题]# #霸气芝士草莓[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪新品[话题]# #饮料[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #果茶[话题]# #草莓味[话题]# #草莓季[话题]# #奈雪の茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1767103086000, "last_update_time": 1767103087000, "user_id": "61693c0b000000000201bc40", "nickname": "碳烤每一只鸽子", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pkvttvmju705ob97g5gjf20lm0bt98", "liked_count": "77", "collected_count": "5", "comment_count": "60", "share_count": "91", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/267d6aedb2fa35b4864edba963347567/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031qnih59kgm005ob97g5gjf20emqlra0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪,霸气芝士草莓,奈雪的茶,奈雪新品,饮料,奶茶,果茶,草莓味,草莓季,奈雪の茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419197, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6953da6e000000001e010145?xsec_token=ABreFM7PEmYQK0Z8qfdDnjNlWUVVzJ1k_WvlCMIxihJdc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABreFM7PEmYQK0Z8qfdDnjNlWUVVzJ1k_WvlCMIxihJdc="}
{"note_id": "67e00a74000000001d017ffa", "type": "normal", "title": "救命，有没有人管管奈雪", "desc": "[扶墙R][扶墙R][扶墙R]一股青汁兑中药的味道，好难喝啊，没有奶味更没有抹茶味，这是我晚上点奶茶的报应吗#奶茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪浓抹黑珍珠[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1742735989000, "last_update_time": 1742735989000, "user_id": "5a5f6ae311be10318fd267d6", "nickname": "奶油咪", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/63a8388f7ffc0f56b9d52165.jpg", "liked_count": "66", "collected_count": "4", "comment_count": "61", "share_count": "9", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/8a962a2ed45b2393e613d0564d966274/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831fcfe2cimq7g4a0tajle6pumngvjo6o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/c86a586f8013b2d23c6a4575474150fe/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831fcfe2cimq804a0tajle6pum5a787k8!nd_dft_wgth_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,奈雪的茶,奈雪浓抹黑珍珠", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419198, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67e00a74000000001d017ffa?xsec_token=AB2n0f3sxqfTjHs0mUwc8P3pvW33UvlGWI2skK8wR-45Q=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB2n0f3sxqfTjHs0mUwc8P3pvW33UvlGWI2skK8wR-45Q="}
