{"note_id": "67602974000000001301af78", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶有不踩雷的品吗", "desc": "为什么点的每一个都好难喝\n之前为了优惠在里面充了钱\n奶茶没奶味没茶味，融合的很差\n果茶都甜的下不了口", "video_url": "", "time": 1734355316000, "last_update_time": 1734355317000, "user_id": "5bd58a51e042910001f70508", "nickname": "怡", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/5bd58a51e042910001f70508.jpg", "liked_count": "61", "collected_count": "12", "comment_count": "38", "share_count": "3", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/eb94cccc0077258aff8b63d838f12eb5/1040g00831bfj9o9dh26g4ble5p552188u1bm9jg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/57c01aeea3fc2d9aaa97f46d4c2ef4d7/1040g00831bfj9o9dh2604ble5p552188teq5ft8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/2cf6aec42a45e0930666e7b1788ad4a7/1040g00831bfj9o9dh25g4ble5p552188iut9bag!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419199, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67602974000000001301af78?xsec_token=ABYN9q_QMJqy8CdQcMv7haTuhYmMN8BuOGPGQ76epnNLE=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABYN9q_QMJqy8CdQcMv7haTuhYmMN8BuOGPGQ76epnNLE="}
{"note_id": "652cae300000000023018e28", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶-鸭屎香珍珠奶茶", "desc": "今天喝（很符合我一贯刻板印象的）\n奈雪的茶—鸭屎香珍珠奶茶（去冰，不加糖）\n自从一年半之前被奈雪深深伤害之后\n我自以为伤口已经堪堪愈合到可以再被撕裂一次的程度\n于是鬼使神差地在低价+开业的双重诱惑之下再次走进奈雪\n因为按理来说，这种不加糖奶茶应该不会有什危险的可能吧\n但是事实再一次证明如果是奈雪的话，那没有什么不可能\n我喝了一口，沉默一路\n喝了两口，沉默一下午\n这杯只有能被舌头尝到的茶味但没茶香 有眼睛能看到的奶白色但是没有奶感\n无论是茶还是奶的粉感都十分的重\n你能感觉到他在客观上确实是奶和茶的混合\n但很奇怪地并不会带来任何的主观愉悦和享受\n尤其是这个软趴趴像果冻一样的珍珠\n没有任何的Q弹和嚼劲吃的我直犯恶心\n真的，哪怕9块钱都不值得\n奈雪我真不知道是你该给我道歉还是我该给你道歉了……\n#奶茶[话题]# #奶茶分享[话题]# #珍珠奶茶[话题]# #奈雪新品奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #鸭屎香[话题]# #难喝[话题]# #珍珠[话题]# #波霸[话题]# #退钱[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1697426992000, "last_update_time": 1697426993000, "user_id": "5ab447c4e8ac2b62bdef7c11", "nickname": "普卡其", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/645359b51c15218568729993.jpg", "liked_count": "60", "collected_count": "6", "comment_count": "36", "share_count": "9", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/41908c1c0b502d77f3a09b98f044002e/1040g00830q9ag7slne004a3r3t3s8v0hpvjvc1g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,奶茶分享,珍珠奶茶,奈雪新品奈雪的茶,奈雪的茶,奈雪,鸭屎香,难喝,珍珠,波霸,退钱", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419199, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/652cae300000000023018e28?xsec_token=ABctHbULT2xn076kP-kbSsNwFilB4jXlD-YDt1hLO1HMg=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABctHbULT2xn076kP-kbSsNwFilB4jXlD-YDt1hLO1HMg="}
{"note_id": "66a60306000000002701211f", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶为什么变成这样了……", "desc": "好难喝…一点质感都没有\n评价是不如雪王\n踢出我的奶茶名单了\n失望\n二编：评论区shut up[飞吻R]客观的评价就我这次买的两杯来说就是毫无质量的糖水，说句没有雪王好就是穷人了公主王子们，你们爱喝喝我不在乎他放的什么东西，口感不好就是不好，高级货调料无人在意^ ^", "video_url": "", "time": 1722155782000, "last_update_time": 1722525482000, "user_id": "60273a2d000000000101d754", "nickname": "Upup", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/62b9552c8441eeb0f4b5e923.jpg", "liked_count": "60", "collected_count": "4", "comment_count": "119", "share_count": "16", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/0050e1138bffab5fb41a1e9db4607420/1040g008315pq3km91e005o1778mgblqk9bbk3b8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419200, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66a60306000000002701211f?xsec_token=ABAaVHpgFClPyxOBwbf7xtGkv_7PworaOPP1Rkoyw1Ydk=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABAaVHpgFClPyxOBwbf7xtGkv_7PworaOPP1Rkoyw1Ydk="}
{"note_id": "69bd327c000000001b022651", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪，你好难喝", "desc": "啥味没有，一嘴冰渣子，还点了一杯大杯的，要不你赔我点钱吧[微笑R][微笑R][微笑R]\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #一喝一个不吱声[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1774006908000, "last_update_time": 1774006909000, "user_id": "5fc6e8bd0000000001008b28", "nickname": "momo", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/63f9866db4f96d52007b0015.jpg", "liked_count": "58", "collected_count": "5", "comment_count": "97", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "广东", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061526/17483d489d2fa37fdc597243fb071594/notes_uhdr/1040g3qo31tuel1326u705nu6t2ug92p865rggu0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,一喝一个不吱声", "last_modify_ts": 1775460419200, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69bd327c000000001b022651?xsec_token=ABk4YV3peSTP3ZCru9_Zl3giyHjf_OX2w-v-WuSS-887o=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABk4YV3peSTP3ZCru9_Zl3giyHjf_OX2w-v-WuSS-887o="}
{"note_id": "68b7f566000000001d016bfe", "type": "normal", "title": "避雷奈雪金色山脉珍珠奶茶！！！", "desc": "以前喝茶味很浓，现在水垮垮一杯！\n奶没有奶味，茶没有茶味！！！\n太难喝了！！！\n以前明明很浓的味道！\n问了店员，说改版了！\n好难喝啊！\n喝了两口扔了！\n@奈雪的茶 你在做什么？好喝的都下架改版了…\n怀念以前的鸭屎香鲜奶茶！怀念西柚气泡茶！\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #避雷贴[话题]# #奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1756886374000, "last_update_time": 1756886375000, "user_id": "599ea3cf6a6a6959d8818d42", "nickname": "糖十七", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31f8dcdsh5s0049olr2hsv3a2l61g3t8", "liked_count": "45", "collected_count": "5", "comment_count": "108", "share_count": "10", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061528/bca18296446397530ffadba92565101f/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831lvaqcmt4qe049olr2hsv3a2fg8f128!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,避雷贴,奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635579, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68b7f566000000001d016bfe?xsec_token=ABBUmvg1aGeT21vsuFx9mCgkblDF7LkcvyFKQcWjkYP20=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABBUmvg1aGeT21vsuFx9mCgkblDF7LkcvyFKQcWjkYP20="}
{"note_id": "695141c30000000022032294", "type": "normal", "title": "不要轻易尝试", "desc": "奈雪的瘦瘦小绿瓶，外出不要轻易尝试，怀疑人生\n堪比西梅汁\n吃了烧烤想喝口解解辣，点了这个，拿着就去日月贝散步了，边走边喝，差点没回来，一路狂奔回酒店\n#一言难尽啊[话题]# #一喝一个不吱声[话题]# #吃完就后悔[话题]# #体验感拉满[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1766932931000, "last_update_time": 1766932931000, "user_id": "5e70bfb80000000001000380", "nickname": "团子团子", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/6434084347807117dee19200.jpg", "liked_count": "40", "collected_count": "9", "comment_count": "78", "share_count": "94", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061528/d7cb5608e39bde778fe643cff820f49a/1040g00831ql1d6iv00e05njgnus080s00ooe34o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "一言难尽啊,一喝一个不吱声,吃完就后悔,体验感拉满", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635580, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/695141c30000000022032294?xsec_token=ABN9kOTARRZwS-OpsDto802owvB6RDKWy1vhZOgsQQs4w=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABN9kOTARRZwS-OpsDto802owvB6RDKWy1vhZOgsQQs4w="}
{"note_id": "69785983000000000a031cf7", "type": "normal", "title": "超浓千层抹 你再取些诈骗的名字试试呢？", "desc": "一个没注意没看配料表，居然加了茉莉茶汤！最讨厌的就是含茉莉味的奶茶....\n取着浓抹的名字，却加些乱七八糟的东西！这股茉莉味完全破坏了抹茶味..浓在哪？我真的get不到..\n\t\n#奈雪[话题]# #超浓千层抹[话题]# #奈雪超浓千层抹[话题]# #奶茶记录[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1769494915000, "last_update_time": 1770776047000, "user_id": "61b76c8600000000100092e9", "nickname": "Y.", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31odihm844s005odndi3414n9uv6re40", "liked_count": "39", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "59", "share_count": "25", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061528/672754fb14d2ad8031d9fb45dfbde8bf/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031sea1ru8le005odndi3414n9m5j69rg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪,超浓千层抹,奈雪超浓千层抹,奶茶记录", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635581, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69785983000000000a031cf7?xsec_token=ABaZUEm0-GlyApSQUJXq6SnGhFmGO_rMKwbDsqdnWh0BY=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABaZUEm0-GlyApSQUJXq6SnGhFmGO_rMKwbDsqdnWh0BY="}
{"note_id": "66b87fac000000000503aeb3", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶受众群体到底是那些啊", "desc": "平时上班只喝沪上的杨枝甘露 今天去古城玩没有沪上 去奈雪的茶买了杨枝甘露 真的一言难尽啊[捂脸R][捂脸R][捂脸R]#吃吃喝喝的日常[话题]# #喝奶茶[话题]# #打工人的快乐周末[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1723367340000, "last_update_time": 1723367340000, "user_id": "5c79071f0000000010009888", "nickname": "杂草🌿", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31np12k4b58b05n3p0sfk16484o6oipg", "liked_count": "34", "collected_count": "5", "comment_count": "85", "share_count": "5", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061528/f451f3ce77f9c22390a4239c0c1bd564/1040g2sg316brqhjb2odg5n3p0sfk1648upuqb58!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061528/ea741f67b4d99c52980c5b956c4294bd/1040g2sg316brqhjb2ocg5n3p0sfk16489toc3v8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "吃吃喝喝的日常,喝奶茶,打工人的快乐周末", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635582, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66b87fac000000000503aeb3?xsec_token=ABBYMPTJTbggyZYqVPkVEJbTqQBBH6mdPYLNUkaHKTreo=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABBYMPTJTbggyZYqVPkVEJbTqQBBH6mdPYLNUkaHKTreo="}
{"note_id": "69afc41d000000001600b50d", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪我恨你现在变得好难喝", "desc": "我会一直点奈雪因为我喜欢喝，但我要一直差评因为现在严重偷工减料，不甜而且太多冰，果酱跟酸奶都变得很少，饮料分层，70%都是冰，其他地方也有这个问题不针对本次点的肇庆某店家，偷工减料应该为总部决策所为，现在对奈雪是又爱又恨\n#奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1773126685000, "last_update_time": 1773128583000, "user_id": "662085300000000003031447", "nickname": "momo", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31sreolhq5k005ph0gko0u5272nti1f0", "liked_count": "27", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "41", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "广东", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/040343b6a6e18e132c097cbfe91b6bc0/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831thasnea68705ph0gko0u5278pcnko8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635582, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69afc41d000000001600b50d?xsec_token=ABCbaO9rNhHBz3jwu7b-OFJYVIBXmsY5PZXKEKiSkrzF0=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABCbaO9rNhHBz3jwu7b-OFJYVIBXmsY5PZXKEKiSkrzF0="}
{"note_id": "683e46e7000000001101cbbd", "type": "normal", "title": "决战奈雪难喝之巅", "desc": "#敢不敢挑战[话题]# #一喝一个不吱声[话题]# #成功与失败[话题]# #不含茶的奶茶[话题]# #一言难尽啊[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #果茶[话题]# #难喝饮料[话题]#\n我感觉他家杨枝甘露，霸气杨梅，霸气葡萄和霸气芝士草莓好喝，其他的果茶奶茶都比较普通。不知道有什么难喝的顺便避避雷，也见识一下大家的口味。不过他可以去茶底，咖啡因敏感的我狂喜。", "video_url": "", "time": 1748911847000, "last_update_time": 1748911847000, "user_id": "62d9eb54000000000e00f8d0", "nickname": "真冬まふゆ", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31ibhah8nge6g5omptda3hu6g7t86to0", "liked_count": "26", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "24", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/6379b2aecdb9ae7237cbc5f8af80e916/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831i8g7kq0n8205omptda3hu6g9nho64o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "敢不敢挑战,一喝一个不吱声,成功与失败,不含茶的奶茶,一言难尽啊,奈雪的茶,奶茶,果茶,难喝饮料", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635583, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/683e46e7000000001101cbbd?xsec_token=ABBHm4r3_efSw6q40IJNtVav6KQHMnkmI1HsscKs0S57k=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABBHm4r3_efSw6q40IJNtVav6KQHMnkmI1HsscKs0S57k="}
{"note_id": "67764ab7000000000900e62d", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪我对你太失望了😡😡", "desc": "奈雪新品补水瓶，一看27一杯，但是对这种鲜榨类型的都很喜欢，所以咬咬牙点了，是我在奈雪喝过最贵的一杯了，之前出的几杯无糖果茶都很好喝，但是当我拿到这杯，一口下去就是苹果汁的味道，夹杂莲雾渣渣和芦荟肉，我真的大失望，花了27买了一杯苹果汁[哭惹R][哭惹R][哭惹R][哭惹R]这个价格下次我选择喝阿嬷手作[生气R]\n#奈雪新品[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1735805623000, "last_update_time": 1735805623000, "user_id": "62cee86d000000000e00ffe2", "nickname": "碎碎念", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo3101gba52ls005omet1mjhvv2riejeeo", "liked_count": "22", "collected_count": "8", "comment_count": "24", "share_count": "18", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/624f3ba9908dd1df3a8aed5f6d77e7a4/1040g2sg31c56rlb3gu705omet1mjhvv27gai7ug!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/1cf1f20c27614d8f5d474d2198a023e1/1040g2sg31c56rlb3gu7g5omet1mjhvv2og7sue8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪新品,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635583, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67764ab7000000000900e62d?xsec_token=ABOStqohIckj5VYL3DjvlDEL0bY02aSZuUsx9cd3GIQFw=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABOStqohIckj5VYL3DjvlDEL0bY02aSZuUsx9cd3GIQFw="}
