{"note_id": "6913117400000000070143ef", "type": "normal", "title": "好看 难喝。", "desc": "奈雪的茶真的让我大失所望。。巨难喝的新品，刚开始没搅拌喝感觉还可以就像轻乳茶的感觉，奶盖一般，后面搅拌均匀喝超级难喝，没有草莓味而且特别寡淡，像融化的冰淇淋然后掺水。。避雷！！#奈雪的茶新品[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶红颜草莓初雪[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1762857332000, "last_update_time": 1762857333000, "user_id": "625a275d000000001000c257", "nickname": "Ue", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31bp9hg9m12505oiq4tek1gin3tt414g", "liked_count": "22", "collected_count": "4", "comment_count": "41", "share_count": "13", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/1bcd0b2eb9d32736fc6c836192f631b0/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031ooa3qvtl2605oiq4tek1gin18vblho!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/8226f5ea7d350fab48fc8b5fd40e909f/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r831ooa1i9tl0dg5oiq4tek1gin10gudio!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶新品,奈雪的茶,奈雪的茶红颜草莓初雪", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635586, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6913117400000000070143ef?xsec_token=ABaoEwewUL6YTlHBzTRVb24dWpnZiLZSdPnR8-DE74JD4=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABaoEwewUL6YTlHBzTRVb24dWpnZiLZSdPnR8-DE74JD4="}
