{"note_id": "6936b484000000001e00f202", "type": "normal", "title": "喝完奈雪草莓初雪整个人都变得淡淡的忧伤", "desc": "沿袭了奈雪一贯的传统 — — 奶盖不多，甚至只有薄薄一层，把白纸掀开几乎就所剩无几了。草莓奶盖没有细腻绵密的奶香味，甚至是我不太喜欢的空气泡沫版奶盖的口感，像泡沫一样一抿就化没有存在感[扯脸H][扯脸H][扯脸H]\n草莓果酱酸酸甜甜的配合底部的米麻薯第一口还有些草莓酸甜味儿，但它家米麻薯有糯米颗粒感，像在吃饭我不喜欢 [抓狂R][抓狂R][抓狂R]\n且茶底寡淡，草莓🍓果酱也没有能很好的融合进去，这一杯红颜草莓初雪既没有果茶的清爽也没有奶茶的醇正 [可怜R][可怜R][可怜R](๑>_<๑)\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶红颜草莓初雪[话题]# #红颜草莓初雪[话题]# #测评[话题]# #喝奶茶[话题]# #草莓味[话题]# #草莓的季节[话题]# #抓住草莓季的尾巴呀[话题]# #一起嚯奶茶[话题]# #冬天的快乐是草莓[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1765192837000, "last_update_time": 1765192837000, "user_id": "5b5bcb93e8ac2b088aac09bb", "nickname": "童话里做英雄！", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pq8mbpel05g4a7jqe5p62drlm1leb0", "liked_count": "17", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "11", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/b631b5f0648c1d2761608287804b74e0/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831pr3ofnojq4g4a7jqe5p62drdpj2d98!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/5d17eb28ebc3e0c010d531827ecd2e37/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831pr3ofnojq404a7jqe5p62drdb4il10!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/6134d4d0e59b6555d178a8c7c227630e/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831pr3ofnojq304a7jqe5p62drl1jjs20!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,奈雪的茶红颜草莓初雪,红颜草莓初雪,测评,喝奶茶,草莓味,草莓的季节,抓住草莓季的尾巴呀,一起嚯奶茶,冬天的快乐是草莓", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635587, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6936b484000000001e00f202?xsec_token=AB8eVl3hJ8qXhJTGclvDw-54zKEv3KUp7JnLc8waUxHhM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB8eVl3hJ8qXhJTGclvDw-54zKEv3KUp7JnLc8waUxHhM="}
{"note_id": "69025d710000000004000d6a", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶你们都是怎么喝下去的", "desc": "一口小绿瓶喇嗓子[汗颜R]拿吸管搅了下还是渣的要命，吸到一块没打碎的酸苹果？牙都要倒了…\n一口杨枝甘露没给我酸死[失望R]没吃过这么酸的芒果\n都少糖了还是很甜…\n其他任何一个牌子都比这玩意儿强吧\n@奈雪的茶", "video_url": "", "time": 1761762673000, "last_update_time": 1761762797000, "user_id": "58ff46dd5e87e71865fdc6b0", "nickname": "salalala1", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo311b56sg1mi0049eda03drhlgiqt3u70", "liked_count": "17", "collected_count": "4", "comment_count": "70", "share_count": "4", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/b2f942bc0e760d4d0a0d27130f0547f4/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031o804jfalm0049eda03drhlg0oc1n6o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061529/61acb9352312b1c091daad26eda849e3/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r031o804hqllm0g49eda03drhlgnen0es8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635588, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69025d710000000004000d6a?xsec_token=ABD2wd7Bd87vaMpGHAQBvowio8ovDDPzhlngUweer4O1o=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABD2wd7Bd87vaMpGHAQBvowio8ovDDPzhlngUweer4O1o="}
{"note_id": "6869f2630000000010013a68", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶避雷版", "desc": "66颗蓝莓桑葚奶昔，不到半小时就分层这样了，喝的速度都赶不上分层的速度，而且桑葚还有股酒精发酵的味道，一尝就是不新鲜的味道#避雷[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1751773795000, "last_update_time": 1751773796000, "user_id": "5c1c3e410000000005012787", "nickname": "开饭了开饭了", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31adsp6dr6o6g5n0s7p0ha9s7fnae83o", "liked_count": "15", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "18", "share_count": "5", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/1ecf3e99f587bb50bc0ff56755cec44c/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031jj4ruauii605n0s7p0ha9s7ltq1080!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/6dda6c1c666748051041fdcc0933f649/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031jj5213n36005n0s7p0ha9s7pmlc8co!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "避雷,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635589, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6869f2630000000010013a68?xsec_token=ABbllcSmfnpvKNU3hg9GjPQAIVYws3fITUuC43Sd66b3Q=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABbllcSmfnpvKNU3hg9GjPQAIVYws3fITUuC43Sd66b3Q="}
{"note_id": "68bed066000000001c032cbc", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶是怎么做到每一个品都那么难喝的", "desc": "点了一杯不加糖血橙西柚，喝下去居然是齁甜齁甜的，其中还有西柚的苦味混在一起。[微笑R][微笑R]n个月之前喝过他家的霸气水果茶，味道也很一般。这次真的的是踩到大雷[微笑R]", "video_url": "", "time": 1757335654000, "last_update_time": 1757335655000, "user_id": "6382154a000000002302a2ec", "nickname": "啊是七月", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31l0ob6epj4cg5os22l58t8ncaq41qto", "liked_count": "12", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "32", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/154a3536ff60bf742e0483aed98a121c/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831m615ruu66dg5os22l58t8ncs80kl9o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635589, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68bed066000000001c032cbc?xsec_token=ABEeOtbLy1xHBGywbcHj1KjFxNvAJU-5yguEBzbQff9vc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABEeOtbLy1xHBGywbcHj1KjFxNvAJU-5yguEBzbQff9vc="}
{"note_id": "68de07ef00000000040286c2", "type": "normal", "title": "到底是谁在捧他？明明就难喝的要鼠🥶", "desc": "这辈子从来没喝过这么寡淡的奶昔\n特别特别稀，还不如满米好喝\n（当然大哥不用说二哥都难喝）\n几乎没有味道\n水汪汪的感觉几乎只有水味\n什么牛油果🥑椰浆几乎尝不到\n关键是也不便宜20入的 真是过分了[生气R]\n而且他定价还是26[汗颜R]怎么敢的\n#奈雪的茶壁垒[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奶昔[话题]# #奶茶壁垒[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #喝不了一点[话题]##超能牛油果酸奶昔[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1759381487000, "last_update_time": 1759387506000, "user_id": "5a6c787fe8ac2b4539d36db1", "nickname": "吾乃天之饺子", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pvp3pd5g4004a144hs7urdhvk6qmug", "liked_count": "12", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "14", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/c74fba2cdba066e46f4aed43799f2926/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831n4ghsplmml04a144hs7urdhpt62r80!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/fe3288b2bb844563e4f92412c340c7a8/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831n4ghsplmmlg4a144hs7urdhsfmfdho!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶壁垒,奶茶,奶昔,奶茶壁垒,奈雪的茶,喝不了一点,超能牛油果酸奶昔", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635590, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68de07ef00000000040286c2?xsec_token=ABgKVNuMcZzafo7skfhp2VUQz-Dn0a0w8eakS8zBloYB0=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABgKVNuMcZzafo7skfhp2VUQz-Dn0a0w8eakS8zBloYB0="}
{"note_id": "65f4584a00000000130261ea", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪你真的太难喝了！！", "desc": "这辈子没喝过这么难喝的奶茶，一口下去像是用白水泡的类似奶粉一样的冲调粉的味道，然后还是那种不舍得给你放的那种感觉。我居然从奶茶里面喝出了白水的味道，也是没谁了。。。我跟我对象说我对象还不信，她也非要尝一尝，结果一口下去面露难色，说为啥能这么淡，奶茶不都用的鲜奶吗？奶味也没有，后调的茶味也没有。。[扯脸H]哦对，我是21点半去买的，我不知道是不是你们着急下班，你们其实可以选择不接单，但是真的很难喝。。。[失望R]#奈雪の茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1710512202000, "last_update_time": 1710512203000, "user_id": "6034a1370000000001009ae6", "nickname": "云生", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/61a59980d569c78027789cdf.jpg", "liked_count": "18", "collected_count": "2", "comment_count": "28", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/77358ee99a6e253431be7a89de31bff4/1040g2sg310ca0lth6i005o1kk4rg96n6pn95n1g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪の茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635590, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/65f4584a00000000130261ea?xsec_token=ABr-hMUy2Ziqr6ULfaIL-MRP0nSVqDNCXqpC6gS1giLZs=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABr-hMUy2Ziqr6ULfaIL-MRP0nSVqDNCXqpC6gS1giLZs="}
{"note_id": "66c6ed00000000001f01b009", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的霸气香水橙子：难评😒", "desc": "属于是一个高开低走了[失望R]\n很少喝奈雪，今天逛街路过进去点了一杯，点的时候我还没有意识到所谓“香水”的威力。\n喝完第一口才看到对于前调中调后调的解释，回味起来感觉还真像那么回事。\n结果越喝橙子味越淡，全是那个香水香精味，而且留在嘴里的味道越来越苦，实在是喝不下去了\n也有可能是我欣赏不来这种设计吧[鄙视R]\n@薯队长 @吃货薯\n#奈雪奈雪的茶[话题]# #果茶[话题]# #霸气香水橙子[话题]# #奈雪香水[话题]# #秋天的第一杯奶茶[话题]# #尝试新口味[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1724312832000, "last_update_time": 1724312832000, "user_id": "6132cb26000000000201af28", "nickname": "清沅", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31cp1k6pmgu6g5o9ipcj0jbp80nts3do", "liked_count": "12", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "6", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/780d07472af5c4e23d8167ce484c1db6/1040g2sg316puljcpk4dg5o9ipcj0jbp8aqj1qlo!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪奈雪的茶,果茶,霸气香水橙子,奈雪香水,秋天的第一杯奶茶,尝试新口味", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635591, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66c6ed00000000001f01b009?xsec_token=AB7zenNqnDbBsG9E7YZJgYb2xyhC2c86EwMZOw5VJXtws=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB7zenNqnDbBsG9E7YZJgYb2xyhC2c86EwMZOw5VJXtws="}
{"note_id": "6623a99e0000000001005742", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶测评", "desc": "⭐⭐热芋泥芋圆奶茶[doge]颜值不错，但甜麻了，喝了一半多，嘴巴很不舒服。这一杯热量近500卡居然，太罪恶了。芋泥还少的可怜，虽是是鲜牛乳（已确证），热量炸球，以后不会再点了。口味真的一般。最后腻的我最后还剩一点没喝完都。米布丁小料是奶香味的布丁，很Q弹，还不错，还便宜，这个还可以。\n⭐⭐⭐青提香乌龙茶[doge]刚进口，淡淡的青提味，回味还有股茶香。感觉很不错。但是，过会以后嘴巴甜甜的贼，避免不了这个糖精。\n⭐⭐⭐⭐手熬黑糖珍珠鲜奶茶[doge] 入口很浓的枣汁和鲜牛乳味，混着黑糖珍珠对来姨妈的女生很友好，上面的奶是淡淡的，下面黑糖珍珠很甜，一定要搅匀再喝。", "video_url": "", "time": 1713613214000, "last_update_time": 1757598527000, "user_id": "632dc55f000000002303ca12", "nickname": "小忆", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo310jie1ha6i5g5opdolfovigi5ot6lto", "liked_count": "11", "collected_count": "2", "comment_count": "4", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/0f4b3634c53e03fbca17beac6e3856f5/1040g2sg311qg2hobn4405opdolfovigidsopd78!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/136006d1ab3c7dfef7cd907235f6d183/1040g2sg311qg2hobn4305opdolfovigi52rcg2o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/35de91b4b35c5dd87a00203996910b14/1040g2sg3160c62lcgo6g5opdolfovigi2ib3jq0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061530/6915eecf816babc2162fdf42239bbefc/1040g00831m9udcevl26g5opdolfovigi2ikea3g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460635591, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6623a99e0000000001005742?xsec_token=ABnQ5ja87oJEQI3AbBx493JC7EoE2XwMuXRG4uRyMdz5E=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABnQ5ja87oJEQI3AbBx493JC7EoE2XwMuXRG4uRyMdz5E="}
{"note_id": "657eac0a000000003801f440", "type": "normal", "title": "为什么喝了嘴里是苦的啊", "desc": "不太懂奶茶，今天点了一杯奈雪的茶的这款【香水茉莉初雪奶茶】，真的觉得不好喝啊，喝了几口就没喝了，而且嘴里还是一股苦味，不知道这款就是这样还是怎么的，有点难受#奶茶分享[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1702800394000, "last_update_time": 1702800394000, "user_id": "5c1c5f0a0000000007014f6c", "nickname": "小张momo杂货铺", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/seller_6974d90fb7f5e20001403794", "liked_count": "19", "collected_count": "3", "comment_count": "11", "share_count": "4", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/5dbff32ce9888aec90c4047e98edc45e/1040g2sg30spcnrgaka005n0sbs51qjrcanctd6g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶分享,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859323, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/657eac0a000000003801f440?xsec_token=ABRlLQavWxi2DE63NBU6c8UKFBkHipLwAWL7DRqEGVUb4=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABRlLQavWxi2DE63NBU6c8UKFBkHipLwAWL7DRqEGVUb4="}
{"note_id": "67ac650d000000002803594a", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪史上最难喝的单品出现了", "desc": "#奈雪的浪漫陪伴   #奈雪雪山玫瑰宝藏茶[话题]#   @奈雪的茶感觉奈雪这一期的周边挺有创意的比较喜欢打算支持下，不爱喝奶茶也点了，结果简直是雷品，这玫瑰花味道让人闻着难受，喝着梗喉，我宁愿失去味觉，看到有人吐槽，没想到是这么难喝的味道，大家喜欢周边不如直接买那个玩偶吧，明明是直接买玩偶，但是要送你一杯奶茶，送了也巨难喝", "video_url": "", "time": 1739351309000, "last_update_time": 1739353396000, "user_id": "5659295ba40e1855220177ff", "nickname": "我是你是我", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/672e2577a19061188b938b11.jpg", "liked_count": "18", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "41", "share_count": "18", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/288a91a3392039547c94e6a6e450ef4c/1040g00831dq2icmsgk0043d67rklmtvvuuvj88g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪雪山玫瑰宝藏茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859325, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67ac650d000000002803594a?xsec_token=ABxcrNeRfIoVj5Ch_EYCtfGBwNQQDtXa7K7iQOHxwOCRs=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABxcrNeRfIoVj5Ch_EYCtfGBwNQQDtXa7K7iQOHxwOCRs="}
{"note_id": "643bae970000000013007497", "type": "normal", "title": "霸气龙井蜜瓜", "desc": "不推荐！！真的是纯冰沙[可怜R][可怜R][可怜R][可怜R][可怜R]味道有点像普通哈密瓜味的饮品[失望R][失望R][失望R][失望R]#奶茶[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #", "video_url": "", "time": 1681632919000, "last_update_time": 1681632920000, "user_id": "58fb5e716a6a697be5f8cb95", "nickname": "刚好我想借一页星云", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/622e0969e0a61eb0c5b5e55c.jpg", "liked_count": "18", "collected_count": "6", "comment_count": "1", "share_count": "3", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/75922539a3fb8ed029c470ff68fe2e49/1000g0082bnt7akogu00049e2r9f73isls9tgikg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/ba25c267b745ea34f97d6886490ea0cd/1000g0082bnt7akogu00g49e2r9f73isl7cv25k8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/c1a79a9407f9b36bcf82adb24bdfe832/1000g0082bnt7akogu01049e2r9f73isltstt6j0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,奈雪", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859326, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/643bae970000000013007497?xsec_token=ABAFXFB9clXgRV9aBrftjK1DAX5W0BcfcuIfOj-cSRS5g=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABAFXFB9clXgRV9aBrftjK1DAX5W0BcfcuIfOj-cSRS5g="}
{"note_id": "6936b484000000001e00f202", "type": "normal", "title": "喝完奈雪草莓初雪整个人都变得淡淡的忧伤", "desc": "沿袭了奈雪一贯的传统 — — 奶盖不多，甚至只有薄薄一层，把白纸掀开几乎就所剩无几了。草莓奶盖没有细腻绵密的奶香味，甚至是我不太喜欢的空气泡沫版奶盖的口感，像泡沫一样一抿就化没有存在感[扯脸H][扯脸H][扯脸H]\n草莓果酱酸酸甜甜的配合底部的米麻薯第一口还有些草莓酸甜味儿，但它家米麻薯有糯米颗粒感，像在吃饭我不喜欢 [抓狂R][抓狂R][抓狂R]\n且茶底寡淡，草莓🍓果酱也没有能很好的融合进去，这一杯红颜草莓初雪既没有果茶的清爽也没有奶茶的醇正 [可怜R][可怜R][可怜R](๑>_<๑)\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶红颜草莓初雪[话题]# #红颜草莓初雪[话题]# #测评[话题]# #喝奶茶[话题]# #草莓味[话题]# #草莓的季节[话题]# #抓住草莓季的尾巴呀[话题]# #一起嚯奶茶[话题]# #冬天的快乐是草莓[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1765192837000, "last_update_time": 1765192837000, "user_id": "5b5bcb93e8ac2b088aac09bb", "nickname": "童话里做英雄！", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pq8mbpel05g4a7jqe5p62drlm1leb0", "liked_count": "17", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "11", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/c107fdc63108c88bf37413f07fa6ff1e/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831pr3ofnojq4g4a7jqe5p62drdpj2d98!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/8728fc61a823e5f66ff7805e14a13e72/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831pr3ofnojq404a7jqe5p62drdb4il10!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/777829bfb16dbd175797b00672e0ef65/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831pr3ofnojq304a7jqe5p62drl1jjs20!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,奈雪的茶红颜草莓初雪,红颜草莓初雪,测评,喝奶茶,草莓味,草莓的季节,抓住草莓季的尾巴呀,一起嚯奶茶,冬天的快乐是草莓", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859326, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6936b484000000001e00f202?xsec_token=AB8eVl3hJ8qXhJTGclvDw-54zKEv3KUp7JnLc8waUxHhM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB8eVl3hJ8qXhJTGclvDw-54zKEv3KUp7JnLc8waUxHhM="}
{"note_id": "69025d710000000004000d6a", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶你们都是怎么喝下去的", "desc": "一口小绿瓶喇嗓子[汗颜R]拿吸管搅了下还是渣的要命，吸到一块没打碎的酸苹果？牙都要倒了…\n一口杨枝甘露没给我酸死[失望R]没吃过这么酸的芒果\n都少糖了还是很甜…\n其他任何一个牌子都比这玩意儿强吧\n@奈雪的茶", "video_url": "", "time": 1761762673000, "last_update_time": 1761762797000, "user_id": "58ff46dd5e87e71865fdc6b0", "nickname": "salalala1", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo311b56sg1mi0049eda03drhlgiqt3u70", "liked_count": "17", "collected_count": "4", "comment_count": "70", "share_count": "4", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/f7c74ff3ae107bc4b7a77dc8dedd3730/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031o804jfalm0049eda03drhlg0oc1n6o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/729228838770037bb6e334fbde9e2197/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r031o804hqllm0g49eda03drhlgnen0es8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859327, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69025d710000000004000d6a?xsec_token=ABD2wd7Bd87vaMpGHAQBvowio8ovDDPzhlngUweer4O1o=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABD2wd7Bd87vaMpGHAQBvowio8ovDDPzhlngUweer4O1o="}
{"note_id": "62b71d0a0000000004002090", "type": "video", "title": "奈雪的茶，新品霸气榴莲巨难喝，就是糖水", "desc": "不要买，不要买，踩雷，巨难喝，就是喝榴莲糖味的糖水，甜的糖尿病都要出来了#长沙[话题]# #奈雪の茶[话题]# #霸气榴莲王[话题]# #榴莲[话题]# #奈雪新品[话题]# #夏日饮品[话题]# #一杯奶茶的快乐[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #网红饮品[话题]#", "video_url": "http://sns-video-hs.xhscdn.com/01e2b71d0a3d4e0e01037003819b49a4ce_259.mp4?sign=3ad143bddbefada3c235754a07ca8a9d&t=69d361a1", "time": 1656167690000, "last_update_time": 1656167690000, "user_id": "5e10a7d90000000001004276", "nickname": "长沙周边游", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/64830d6465ab555217ca62a2.jpg", "liked_count": "15", "collected_count": "6", "comment_count": "2", "share_count": "5", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/2923acf6e14788ede5240495287ea76b/ef71027a-c6ae-3421-8681-aa72d6d3533b!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "长沙,奈雪の茶,霸气榴莲王,榴莲,奈雪新品,夏日饮品,一杯奶茶的快乐,奶茶,网红饮品", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859328, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/62b71d0a0000000004002090?xsec_token=AB8nzPxL0LPBumQgheJpGjjVaR4VQJkXnpSz2gRp04TM4=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB8nzPxL0LPBumQgheJpGjjVaR4VQJkXnpSz2gRp04TM4="}
{"note_id": "688b61e4000000002303ae2f", "type": "normal", "title": "测评奈雪的茶【霸气不加糖黑葡萄】", "desc": "💜省流版：不好喝！不推荐！\n\t\n❤️本人喝奶茶爱好：喜欢料多的，不喜欢太甜的。基于这个测评的。\n\t\n❤️详细描述：\n1⃣葡萄果肉极其少！还很碎。（我买的是14.6元，不如买两串葡萄🍇吃吃）椰果也少。总体很稀。\n\t\n2⃣不能选甜度，好甜好甜，我平时点奶茶都是不另外加糖的。所以这款喝着好像糖水！（又甜又稀的果汁🍹）\n总之真的不推荐。。\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #霸气不加糖黑葡萄[话题]# #奶茶分享[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]# #喝不腻的果茶[话题]# #北京奶茶店[话题]# #果茶测评[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶测评[话题]# #果茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1753965028000, "last_update_time": 1754833772000, "user_id": "5e19d1b8000000000100a094", "nickname": "刘阿姨", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31cj0oegqgm405ngpq6s0984khusk9p0", "liked_count": "13", "collected_count": "5", "comment_count": "6", "share_count": "9", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/c1a2173a3979bd02d45a5a5a3bf474b0/1040g00831kjpu6omiu505ngpq6s0984ks28d1fg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/1e59e34999b81b0bfbb8cb68076fcc36/1040g00831kjpu6omiu5g5ngpq6s0984kg3hnsd8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061532/be2601042b2a250d876268dbcf5fd3d3/1040g00831kjpu6omiu605ngpq6s0984kit503o8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,霸气不加糖黑葡萄,奶茶分享,奶茶测评,喝不腻的果茶,北京奶茶店,果茶测评,奶茶,奈雪的茶测评,果茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859328, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/688b61e4000000002303ae2f?xsec_token=ABTwPx90H9h68taBTOog7ATaqQ3ofrhb0Su-IL9YNPeaE=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABTwPx90H9h68taBTOog7ATaqQ3ofrhb0Su-IL9YNPeaE="}
{"note_id": "67f76d7e000000000b01dfe4", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪浓抹黑珍珠避雷👎难喝！一点都不浓", "desc": "一点都对不起这个名字，不如1、、的抹茶➕珍珠，点家的抹茶起码很浓郁，奈雪这个好淡好淡，没啥抹茶味…（虽然我点的是不加糖，但是感觉加了糖也不会好喝到哪去[石化R]\n#奶茶测评[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪新品[话题]# #奈雪的茶难喝[话题]# #奈雪浓抹黑珍珠[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1744268670000, "last_update_time": 1744268670000, "user_id": "5b02450d11be10300c65771b", "nickname": "星星日记", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31u5etapvig0g4a5gok2gqtor63aqh18", "liked_count": "14", "collected_count": "4", "comment_count": "7", "share_count": "4", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061533/04a15bce1b913676e0190b578debfb1d/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031g3a8a1v02004a5gok2gqtor1t561p8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶测评,奶茶,奈雪,奈雪的茶,奈雪新品,奈雪的茶难喝,奈雪浓抹黑珍珠", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859329, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67f76d7e000000000b01dfe4?xsec_token=ABI_LyWM-_jV20JoyR-bhV8Pr4rr9NY1oMe-2nPo6tA60=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABI_LyWM-_jV20JoyR-bhV8Pr4rr9NY1oMe-2nPo6tA60="}
{"note_id": "68bed066000000001c032cbc", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶是怎么做到每一个品都那么难喝的", "desc": "点了一杯不加糖血橙西柚，喝下去居然是齁甜齁甜的，其中还有西柚的苦味混在一起。[微笑R][微笑R]n个月之前喝过他家的霸气水果茶，味道也很一般。这次真的的是踩到大雷[微笑R]", "video_url": "", "time": 1757335654000, "last_update_time": 1757335655000, "user_id": "6382154a000000002302a2ec", "nickname": "啊是七月", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31l0ob6epj4cg5os22l58t8ncaq41qto", "liked_count": "12", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "32", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061533/637226a67d45b4810dd986612ff225d9/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831m615ruu66dg5os22l58t8ncs80kl9o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859330, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68bed066000000001c032cbc?xsec_token=ABEeOtbLy1xHBGywbcHj1KjFxNvAJU-5yguEBzbQff9vc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABEeOtbLy1xHBGywbcHj1KjFxNvAJU-5yguEBzbQff9vc="}
{"note_id": "68de07ef00000000040286c2", "type": "normal", "title": "到底是谁在捧他？明明就难喝的要鼠🥶", "desc": "这辈子从来没喝过这么寡淡的奶昔\n特别特别稀，还不如满米好喝\n（当然大哥不用说二哥都难喝）\n几乎没有味道\n水汪汪的感觉几乎只有水味\n什么牛油果🥑椰浆几乎尝不到\n关键是也不便宜20入的 真是过分了[生气R]\n而且他定价还是26[汗颜R]怎么敢的\n#奈雪的茶壁垒[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奶昔[话题]# #奶茶壁垒[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #喝不了一点[话题]##超能牛油果酸奶昔[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1759381487000, "last_update_time": 1759387506000, "user_id": "5a6c787fe8ac2b4539d36db1", "nickname": "吾乃天之饺子", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pvp3pd5g4004a144hs7urdhvk6qmug", "liked_count": "12", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "14", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061533/59e18a1064203d61aa2daeb35d9c2b84/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831n4ghsplmml04a144hs7urdhpt62r80!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061533/0ba1c0ac581dd2b77c7fc015208d62b0/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831n4ghsplmmlg4a144hs7urdhsfmfdho!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶壁垒,奶茶,奶昔,奶茶壁垒,奈雪的茶,喝不了一点,超能牛油果酸奶昔", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859330, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68de07ef00000000040286c2?xsec_token=ABgKVNuMcZzafo7skfhp2VUQz-Dn0a0w8eakS8zBloYB0=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABgKVNuMcZzafo7skfhp2VUQz-Dn0a0w8eakS8zBloYB0="}
