{"note_id": "64f308bc000000001500812c", "type": "video", "title": "奶茶新品测评｜奈雪你睡了吗？反正我睡不着", "desc": "#吃了甜食会开心[话题]#\n🥤宝宝们！我喝奶茶竟然踩雷了！！！\n🥤点了奈雪家的新品荔枝玫瑰水牛乳奶茶，看这名字应该超好喝对吧？结果我就呵呵了[汗颜R][汗颜R][汗颜R]\n🥤荔枝玫瑰水牛乳奶茶（去冰少少糖，➕芝士）\n✅它：茶底不香，它：一股香精味，它：颜值满分实则非常一般\n✅我：不会回购，而且非常失望[抓狂R][抓狂R][抓狂R]\n🥤奈雪！你要是再不用心做产品，会失去更多宝宝！\n#美食[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]# #奶茶分享[话题]# #奈雪新品[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #奶茶推荐[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# @吃货薯 @视频薯 @小红书视频号 @小红书创作学院", "video_url": "http://sns-video-hs.xhscdn.com/stream/110/259/01e4f308bb314c2a010371038a555a6416_259.mp4?sign=b8a2c99a0a81a334bdabd1a88e945df7&t=69d361f3", "time": 1693649084000, "last_update_time": 1693649085000, "user_id": "5a4b735b4eacab4b050d1f68", "nickname": "爱吃贪玩的阿舒", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/64033483d0695d8b046ed667.jpg", "liked_count": "9", "collected_count": "3", "comment_count": "1", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061534/57d40c0613263888c5ccba754f1ccf8a/1040g00830oh11r4e24004a0kc5plm7r8vafclug!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "吃了甜食会开心,美食,奶茶,奶茶测评,奶茶分享,奈雪新品,奈雪,奶茶推荐,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859336, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/64f308bc000000001500812c?xsec_token=ABAGxppARuOWr9vpQdc6WKGWCzXHtbh-P7dZfDkuOwD4w=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABAGxppARuOWr9vpQdc6WKGWCzXHtbh-P7dZfDkuOwD4w="}
{"note_id": "646725f8000000002701284b", "type": "normal", "title": "贪便宜的大怨种＝我😩请避雷", "desc": "这玩意真的是人可以喝的吗\n这真的是奈雪的产品吗\n真的踩雷\n十分难喝\n前面又酸又难喝，喝到后面还发苦\n里面难道有一块柠檬吗[失望R][失望R][失望R]\n#奈雪奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1684481528000, "last_update_time": 1684481529000, "user_id": "5c0109ac51783a22108268fe", "nickname": "🍩", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31ginse25386g4bun1r4qoq7u80j2450", "liked_count": "13", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "27", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061534/9831ebcbc44b065c07f8631e86000c8f/1000g0082h1mgiicii06g4bun1r4qoq7utg7cel8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061534/ed5b86d6f7015bf8e300d22beacfb3db/1000g0082h1mgiicii05g4bun1r4qoq7uiv31jng!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775460859336, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/646725f8000000002701284b?xsec_token=ABOnl1ZUN1Z2J4XgdSHDiUkiNiHPhUJWq4i6VSBsTqPTQ=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABOnl1ZUN1Z2J4XgdSHDiUkiNiHPhUJWq4i6VSBsTqPTQ="}
