{"note_id": "65bf07bc000000002c03e3e5", "type": "normal", "title": "23的奶茶为啥会这么难喝！！！避雷奈雪的茶", "desc": "真的不要太难喝啊\n看了下配料 就是放的樱桃汁\n清汤寡水的\n就那么几颗车厘子就买我23是吧[捂脸R]\n记得几年前的奈雪明明都挺好喝的\n现在二十➕的奶茶 还没得蜜雪好喝[哭惹R]\n狠狠避雷了！！！\n#奶茶[话题]# #奶茶避雷[话题]# #奈雪[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1707018172000, "last_update_time": 1707018173000, "user_id": "6188f5950000000010006971", "nickname": "🐘", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo30p73707546005oc8umak0qbhi3fspr8", "liked_count": "9", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "32", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061536/d5283c49af25f110282efc7abd7ad844/1040g2sg30uo7tqo05i005oc8umak0qbhhrvj450!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,奶茶避雷,奈雪", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066181, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/65bf07bc000000002c03e3e5?xsec_token=ABewcOyeRwU_1Nv3bCYhSXzYMvMsEW8tvGVMv-GDn6inI=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABewcOyeRwU_1Nv3bCYhSXzYMvMsEW8tvGVMv-GDn6inI="}
