{"note_id": "68807d6500000000120309db", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶 浓抹黑珍珠", "desc": "记第一次喝到这么难喝的抹茶制品\n以前只喝过它家的果茶 第一次尝试这个\n选的是默认的少甜 正常冰\n一口下去回到小学喝的五毛钱一杯的珍珠奶茶\n完全没有抹茶味 甜度比纯牛奶多一点点甜\n很腻 是像金币巧克力那种代可可脂的腻\n原本想着别浪费奶茶额度怎么也得喝完\n实在喝不下去 扔了[哭惹R][哭惹R][哭惹R]\n\t\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #难喝奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1753251173000, "last_update_time": 1753251173000, "user_id": "5b04cbde11be104dbed43462", "nickname": "米宗星球备忘录", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31men2ca2686g4a5iom5tsd320bfatcg", "liked_count": "7", "collected_count": "2", "comment_count": "16", "share_count": "2", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061536/80279f71faa770e2255cb3ec587b1663/1040g2sg31k95hkp72od04a5iom5tsd320uq1kdo!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,难喝奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066183, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68807d6500000000120309db?xsec_token=ABfeu8Flb8I9DrBSTLH522d86DmYTtAi00s8fl3OEY8l0=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABfeu8Flb8I9DrBSTLH522d86DmYTtAi00s8fl3OEY8l0="}
{"note_id": "657852da000000003a00e598", "type": "normal", "title": "不要靠近🙅🏻‍♀️，会变得不幸", "desc": "奈雪的罗汉果甜，他们的研发真的有喝过吗[扶墙R][扶墙R][扶墙R]好难喝啊！！！第一次喝奶茶喝得想yue，顺带开始讨厌罗汉果了[石化R][石化R][石化R]我寻思着罗汉果泡水还挺好喝的，怎么放进奶茶里这么一言难尽啊！[失望R][失望R][失望R]\n\t\n#奶茶踩雷[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #代糖[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1702384346000, "last_update_time": 1702384346000, "user_id": "56020617a75c954fc1f2306d", "nickname": "条条子的坨", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo311nmcf4d7200416rob31ec3dtl97kg0", "liked_count": "7", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "7", "share_count": "6", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061536/20771eb38265e231ead69bd1b065c491/1040g00830sj6be8njm00416rob31ec3d8861dk0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶踩雷,奈雪,代糖,奶茶,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066184, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/657852da000000003a00e598?xsec_token=ABnmh4SDBdW43eMRrCxA4OvGg0o-Xn0kLHg02CQ9CduD8=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABnmh4SDBdW43eMRrCxA4OvGg0o-Xn0kLHg02CQ9CduD8="}
