{"note_id": "67d0f123000000002503e6b4", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪已经不是曾经的奈雪了", "desc": "好难喝啊？我以前可是最喜欢金色山脉奶茶这个系列的   后来出了很多新的奶茶就很久没喝过奈雪   今天突然很想喝点了一杯  难喝到无法形容  真的是茶没茶味奶没奶味   第一口还发酸   我甚至觉得茶底是不是坏了[叹气R][叹气R]奶盖也不浓郁   加进去和没有差不多[笑哭R][笑哭R]就真的和我自己旺仔加茉莉花茶差不多那种寡淡[失望R][失望R][失望R]失望了再见吧奈雪[再见R]#奶茶[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪金色山脉奶茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶难喝[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1741746467000, "last_update_time": 1741746467000, "user_id": "59c2751a51783a1eba98de76", "nickname": "没撒盐的秋刀鱼🎏", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo3131svhnrk20049qo7sqhlnjml40jk10", "liked_count": "7", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "27", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061536/b3ab5f8b025f8890350406561a636537/1040g2sg31etnlofmls7049qo7sqhlnjm2qo6jko!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,奶茶测评,奈雪的茶,奈雪金色山脉奶茶,奈雪的茶难喝", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066185, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67d0f123000000002503e6b4?xsec_token=ABqCxoVglG0RH0Yronmr8NuBUpfAF0VsOLq17j1aMghoM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABqCxoVglG0RH0Yronmr8NuBUpfAF0VsOLq17j1aMghoM="}
{"note_id": "67c7f4ea0000000029036c51", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的珍珠奶茶不好喝", "desc": "我平时不怎么喝奶茶，喝果茶比较多，喝的话也只爱喝珍珠奶茶，但是奈雪的这个珍珠就是软趴趴的，一点嚼劲都没有，还是喜茶的珍珠奶茶好喝啊，奈雪的果茶还挺好喝，珍珠真的不太行，不会再回购了", "video_url": "", "time": 1741157610000, "last_update_time": 1741168086000, "user_id": "5e6496c10000000001005140", "nickname": "后来📷", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo3152idk9f0m005nj4ir0g8ka0agc0h18", "liked_count": "6", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061536/d2d1821c6f0675344a0d5ba524bc1e79/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031ekuqc42ku005nj4ir0g8ka0a52habg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066186, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67c7f4ea0000000029036c51?xsec_token=ABaa55rQMQMEGjF8Pfhupduy_J67yCjd_tRK98TbMtH0k=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABaa55rQMQMEGjF8Pfhupduy_J67yCjd_tRK98TbMtH0k="}
