{"note_id": "660816f4000000001b00807b", "type": "normal", "title": "我可能点到了奈雪最难喝的茶…..", "desc": "选了少少甜真的是我自作自受……\n味道像是洗洁精没有冲干净的刷锅水\n促进肠道蠕动的功能倒是十分强大，喝了1/4左右，就立刻窜了……", "video_url": "", "time": 1711806196000, "last_update_time": 1711806196000, "user_id": "5a2ffcbae8ac2b1372c17547", "nickname": "momo", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31o34rg72mg004a0886ubkta7nl4339o", "liked_count": "5", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "18", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061537/256c3f60462eaa4a53875ccfbcba6a2c/1040g2sg310vj1fnr6o004a0886ubkta7eg4t73o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066188, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/660816f4000000001b00807b?xsec_token=AB9yR0UJvP306Z9MEV1ABzuHHPDW818FVwbmKbpiYVkeY=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB9yR0UJvP306Z9MEV1ABzuHHPDW818FVwbmKbpiYVkeY="}
{"note_id": "68393689000000000303d941", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪还我正常的霸气葡萄❗️❗️❗️", "desc": "以前巨喜欢喝奈雪 每天都点\n霸气葡萄一天喝好几杯\n我不喜欢喝齁甜的 所以经典款霸气葡萄的不另外加糖就特别好❗️❗️\n奈雪搞了那个不加糖系列没多久 就把经典款的霸气葡萄霸气草莓啥的都给下架了[哭惹R]这个不加糖系列真的是超级齁甜难喝！\n@奈雪的茶 @奈雪的茶（宠粉版）不止我一个人觉得不加糖系列不如经典款 你快点把经典款那些重新上架吧！！！\n这个冬天你就顾着搞你那个死难喝的不加糖系列了 连巨好喝的耙耙柑你居然都忘回归了[微笑R]\n\t\n#果茶爱好者[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #果茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #奈雪の茶[话题]# #水果茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1748579977000, "last_update_time": 1748579978000, "user_id": "54f541dbd39ea2517ab525e0", "nickname": "『陈不辣』", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31i3s983s7e004027qn0tm9f0im9vth8", "liked_count": "5", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "5", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061537/bf85f536a62110a8654f2f2a074957cf/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831i3hmfrh70804027qn0tm9f009ufs08!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "果茶爱好者,奶茶测评,奶茶,果茶,奈雪的茶,奈雪,奈雪の茶,水果茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066188, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68393689000000000303d941?xsec_token=ABh_XohfCYA6IilbyaYnW0sJXAlD9FU6SfcZTw4_phws4=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABh_XohfCYA6IilbyaYnW0sJXAlD9FU6SfcZTw4_phws4="}
{"note_id": "65eef39600000000140040f4", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪品控真是越来越差", "desc": "好久没喝，充的卡一直没用完，路过买了杯热粑粑柑要了个三分糖，茶味完全没喝出来，甜到牙疼的程度，那标准做法是什么？？怀疑是制作员工根本没有按三分糖的标准，要么就是品控不行#奈雪[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #三分糖[话题]#\n这不是第一次发生三分糖甜死人了，真有人能喝完整杯奈雪吗？", "video_url": "", "time": 1710158742000, "last_update_time": 1710158948000, "user_id": "555c40cb62a60c4136e6fdca", "nickname": "momo", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31in6e2q3ha0040l8en0cnvea88gj3u8", "liked_count": "5", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "25", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061537/c3bf212ff64c0b01ba14b3c00ba6aae2/1040g00831071fav65s0040l8en0cnveafhmeg88!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪,奈雪的茶,三分糖", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066189, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/65eef39600000000140040f4?xsec_token=ABRHgBLvZ7qtmpnLR9t-7bmMfwlKe233GrzXDM9BoU-gM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABRHgBLvZ7qtmpnLR9t-7bmMfwlKe233GrzXDM9BoU-gM="}
