{"note_id": "6863f7ad0000000020019c74", "type": "normal", "title": "喝奶茶居然喝emo", "desc": "奈雪的浓抹黑珍珠，实在是太太太太太太难喝了！！！！！离谱啊，抹茶的味道很淡，一股冲了很多水的味道，买回来放到现在也没说服自己喝完[哭惹R][哭惹R][哭惹R]，本来只想尝个鲜，没想到爆了个大雷[生气R][生气R][生气R]\n\t\n#奶茶[话题]# #抹茶奶茶[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1751381933000, "last_update_time": 1751381933000, "user_id": "61de18f80000000010007abc", "nickname": "momo", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pv6e0nm7u605oeu33s40ulsrc3l76o", "liked_count": "4", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "1", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061537/21b4a234f9a2b47fbef736240e854ea9/1040g2sg31jda102bj03g5oeu33s40ulsp022368!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,抹茶奶茶,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066190, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6863f7ad0000000020019c74?xsec_token=AB15aJ47fzA4vNnkBp2DTKUGMhMmpGc1K4-U5RQD9J7bM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB15aJ47fzA4vNnkBp2DTKUGMhMmpGc1K4-U5RQD9J7bM="}
{"note_id": "66053381000000001203d891", "type": "video", "title": "踩雷奈雪新品龙井奶盖 #冤种", "desc": "❌#奈雪新品[话题]# #奈雪龙井春茶[话题]# 这个雷我替你们先踩了\n\t\n茶底茶味比较涩，奶盖味也很淡，可能主要突出一个茶香吧\n看宣传图还以为有什么料，其实就是一个纯茶底。大杯的杯子是没有印花的，中杯的有就好看很多。\n🤦🏻‍♀️别买", "video_url": "http://sns-video-hs.xhscdn.com/stream/110/259/01e6053380134266010373038e84521c3f_259.mp4?sign=101a4f0ae9a24be0f469e2b6ae295205&t=69d362c8", "time": 1711616897000, "last_update_time": 1711616897000, "user_id": "56906ed5aed75816022cba47", "nickname": "粉一枚", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo310b90rpqme0g452i9indbei7um8tsno", "liked_count": "5", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "3", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061537/b27f1e92590dc6dd71a94a635b41c55c/1040g008310soogjf6g00452i9indbei7ahknr6g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪新品,奈雪龙井春茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461066190, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66053381000000001203d891?xsec_token=ABWkMvNjJFR5wstakesWDDH4aDKOlYGYw2FOGiU9FIa3k=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABWkMvNjJFR5wstakesWDDH4aDKOlYGYw2FOGiU9FIa3k="}
{"note_id": "65251a00000000001f0382bd", "type": "normal", "title": "避雷奈雪霸气石榴", "desc": "前排叠甲：奈雪老粉，每次出新品基本都会去喝\n——\n奈雪你自己看看你这石榴好喝吗？？？\n少少甜还齁甜+没有石榴味，像在喝糖水\n本就少得可怜的石榴还飘在上面，为什么会飘在上面？因为表皮是碎的，饱满的石榴都是沉在底下的[微笑R]\n就这还卖我22一杯，真茶屋的芝士石榴跟你差不多价我能用勺子吃半天！！！你这石榴我猛喝三大口还没喝到一颗！！！\n@奈雪的茶 19年爱上你家霸气草莓，逢人推荐\n这次真的失望透顶。\n#奈雪[话题]# #奈雪霸气系列[话题]# #奈雪霸气东方石榴[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1696930304000, "last_update_time": 1697452226000, "user_id": "5b8a8b3ba6b1780001c3a19f", "nickname": "🥐", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31jorl0dsiu004ao1jr5jn8cvsg8hoc8", "liked_count": "4", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "4", "share_count": "4", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061539/ef32726184eaddb0db2e5b6e3938ca02/1040g00830q1t0f32na0g4ao1jr5jn8cv3s6sev0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061539/34bc9d02ed03f86bf9b967e914cb6b34/1040g00830q1t0f32na104ao1jr5jn8cv6sht5k8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪,奈雪霸气系列,奈雪霸气东方石榴", "last_modify_ts": 1775461265535, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/65251a00000000001f0382bd?xsec_token=ABFJ2hOnLYCgF9hFvBJuzHWeIFoTXrnfvdFjf9UOVL0FY=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABFJ2hOnLYCgF9hFvBJuzHWeIFoTXrnfvdFjf9UOVL0FY="}
