{"note_id": "6858fdcf00000000230053af", "type": "normal", "title": "吐槽🤮纯吐🤮奈雪的茶", "desc": "我头一次吐槽饮料…真的真的\n在我的认知范围里，饮料不会多难喝，个人口味问题而已。\n但是某雪的茶，让我重新认知了饮料世界！\n咋能做的这么难喝！都难喝出新高度了！\n一口就一口差不点给我送走！\n明明是柠檬红茶但是是如假包换的消毒水味！\n喝它，不是解渴，是洗胃，能洗的贼彻底#柠檬茶[话题]# #毒茶茶茶茶茶茶[话题]##饮料分享[话题]# ##饮品爱好者[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1750662607000, "last_update_time": 1750665568000, "user_id": "5ea7ff71000000000100a29c", "nickname": "记录日子我和你", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo315cif94dha005nl7vtog98ksi2jqmto", "liked_count": "4", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "14", "share_count": "4", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061540/940ce2b96b7e965a1c7ec0c7a75d74a0/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031j2j0d1h1e005nl7vtog98kse0uig4g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "柠檬茶,毒茶茶茶茶茶茶,饮料分享,饮品爱好者", "last_modify_ts": 1775461265540, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6858fdcf00000000230053af?xsec_token=ABBYccMVStSvhcl5CfQrHDGn0hxwjK4_WmbFJGBI31--E=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABBYccMVStSvhcl5CfQrHDGn0hxwjK4_WmbFJGBI31--E="}
