{"note_id": "68038e66000000001e00ada4", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶行不行啊，这么难喝，便宜也不能这么难喝吧\n#奈雪的茶[话题]#", "desc": "奈雪的茶行不行啊，这么难喝，便宜也不能这么难喝吧\n#奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1745063526000, "last_update_time": 1745063527000, "user_id": "6366241d000000001f018250", "nickname": "红薯红薯大红薯", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/d784fc20c996f3d2f39d034c404f234e.jpg", "liked_count": "3", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "7", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061540/17c8a1cd8e96df663091ee121c01c271/1040g00831gf591s33i005or64genr0ig7hjl4fg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461265542, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68038e66000000001e00ada4?xsec_token=AB-HgvGXvKV8S70msBFOqiqeBxAdSFvLjeBRNeD19sjqc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB-HgvGXvKV8S70msBFOqiqeBxAdSFvLjeBRNeD19sjqc="}
{"note_id": "69d1ce65000000001a0363c7", "type": "normal", "title": "莲雾补糖小粉瓶-暂定个人年度奈雪最差", "desc": "奈雪的茶这款新的莲雾补水小粉瓶让我非常失望。\n\t\n冰沙款首先无糖度可调，吸管插下去，一口闷上来和纯糖水一样甜，恍如混果汁一般。真的大呼上当，个人非常不喜欢。好不容易整完了糖浆，然后下来就是淡寡无味的冰沙时间，整体口感比较割裂。\n\t\n整体莲雾的量也不多，不用指望像66颗蓝莓那样有很多颗粒，切成了很细碎的微型的颗粒，如果能在底部垫起来，大概平铺0.8-1厘米左右，所以果肉吃起来也不够过瘾。前面冲锋的糖味，将莲雾的特有风味压制的毫无翻身之力。只有在吸入最后的微型颗粒的时候，才能如往事般轻轻回味。还带着难绷的糖后余涩。\n\t\n很少觉得很不能打的，但这款真的给不了好评，真心很难喝。\n就不要说补水了，补的是糖水！好不好。\n\t\n暂时预定年度最差喜茶单品莲雾~~~\n\t\n#喝不腻的果茶[话题]# #给我一杯果茶[话题]# #果茶爱好者[话题]# #不额外加糖[话题]# #果茶[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]# #奶茶[话题]# #奈雪[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #奈雪新品[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1775357541000, "last_update_time": 1775357812000, "user_id": "5d497c68000000001602153b", "nickname": "San", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31u10bt14720g5na9fhk5k59rmms51oo", "liked_count": "3", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "广东", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061540/c11bce33b6c765de25c6fb609e317556/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r031uiikss52i605na9fhk5k59r0p1e3co!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061540/e2d6b4828cb4f4a7dd293aa4c87e6024/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r031uiikss52i405na9fhk5k59rrbvfmqg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061540/830cca10aa702255e95cd5e5f7f25f67/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r031uiikss52i5g5na9fhk5k59rmj3odng!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "喝不腻的果茶,给我一杯果茶,果茶爱好者,不额外加糖,果茶,奶茶测评,奶茶,奈雪,奈雪的茶,奈雪新品", "last_modify_ts": 1775461265543, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69d1ce65000000001a0363c7?xsec_token=ABhpi4ZCfxv3H8sNGfio8WqU3TuQTdNcvxBCmZ-WPf62k=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABhpi4ZCfxv3H8sNGfio8WqU3TuQTdNcvxBCmZ-WPf62k="}
{"note_id": "64647e440000000013030895", "type": "video", "title": "奈雪，再这样下去等着倒闭吧！！", "desc": "还记得多年前第一次被奈雪家的霸气杨梅惊艳！那种满口果肉和奶盖冰沙融合在一起的丰富口感！念念不忘！后来越来越觉得他家敷衍难喝，直到今天再次尝试点霸气杨梅，这什么鬼啊！！一杯冰水飘着点杨梅肉！快吐了！就是这么糊弄消费者的？？！！太气人了！#奈雪[话题]# #杨梅冰沙[话题]# #奈雪の茶[话题]#", "video_url": "http://sns-video-hs.xhscdn.com/stream/110/259/01e4647e44ba1baf0103730388288da142_259.mp4?sign=1a3d232b0e6956ef868eaa9b58b8e11c&t=69d36379", "time": 1684307524000, "last_update_time": 1684307525000, "user_id": "557192a542099574dadfc01d", "nickname": "lucky930cn", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31u31spus720040o9r99abg0t63er6so", "liked_count": "4", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061540/c697d31928077f7812772bf30746f66c/1000g0082gnailkuii00040o9r99abg0ttc3qhco!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪,杨梅冰沙,奈雪の茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461265543, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/64647e440000000013030895?xsec_token=ABZbTNlCQtL3NovaidP0aZYxPAQyS-MUkhY6Q5YOhi6tE=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABZbTNlCQtL3NovaidP0aZYxPAQyS-MUkhY6Q5YOhi6tE="}
