{"note_id": "697766f5000000002800a1cc", "type": "normal", "title": "对奶茶祛魅了", "desc": "奈雪的可可熔岩慕斯，个人觉得味道一般吧，有点寡淡，巧克力味道不浓，小料还不错，有珍珠跟可可冻。\n\t\n感觉这几年自己对奶茶的热爱程度直线下降，可能是因为奶茶喝了容易腻，一杯喝下去基本上喝了个水饱，而且有些奶茶喝了晚上还睡不着。果茶呢，喝来喝去也就那几种，还没有纯果汁好喝。现在不同奶茶店出各种各样的新品，味道感觉大差不差，没意思。\n#奶茶[话题]# #不喝奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1769432821000, "last_update_time": 1769432822000, "user_id": "5dbbfc4b0000000001001bac", "nickname": "生姜润喉糖", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/627bd9beee3d1dc1f7da18ad.jpg", "liked_count": "2", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "8", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061541/0c56724c703e3c08496606f719c222d3/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r031rq0dkuoj2605ndrvh5g86tce31o0f8!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶,不喝奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461265546, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/697766f5000000002800a1cc?xsec_token=ABle3VOnJvZ-gbGNL2fhmBozdpJI3_vjkCXcYUqKXfzhQ=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABle3VOnJvZ-gbGNL2fhmBozdpJI3_vjkCXcYUqKXfzhQ="}
