{"note_id": "66ea97f2000000001e01bb9a", "type": "normal", "title": "为什么这么难喝", "desc": "#奈雪奈雪的茶[话题]#\n喝了一口，满嘴清凉的香精味\n手捣柠檬茶\n一个字都不能信[哭惹R]\n可能心理比较反感，喝了半杯都感觉要yue了\n有啥说的吗", "video_url": "", "time": 1726650354000, "last_update_time": 1726650354000, "user_id": "633e65c200000000180282c1", "nickname": "炒股能赚钱", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/633e65c200000000180282c1.jpg", "liked_count": "8", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "3", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061543/21740636ae42cfc97ddff61a7cf34063/1040g008317sp9brs3k6g5opucn1650m1ts94djo!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461466917, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66ea97f2000000001e01bb9a?xsec_token=ABRlO8aZZ7AXnjGO4tvGHhaRExCLFXC3E2-TYqltJmBz4=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABRlO8aZZ7AXnjGO4tvGHhaRExCLFXC3E2-TYqltJmBz4="}
