{"note_id": "67f8b528000000001d027ddc", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪新品避雷针！！！巨难喝", "desc": "#奈雪的茶[话题]# #奶昔[话题]# #抹茶[话题]#\n第一次喝到那么难喝的奶昔，那是奶昔吗?是不是对奶昔有什么误解。有冰沙的感觉吗?没有!要不要跟茉酸奶报个课。跟水一样稀，还不满杯。奶昔不像奶昔，奶茶不像奶茶，果茶不像果茶，冰沙又不是冰沙，简直一无是处，少少甜简直跟我速冲加多了水没什么区别。抹茶味没有，奶昔味也没有。第一次这么无语#奶茶测评[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1744352552000, "last_update_time": 1744352846000, "user_id": "64002ae4000000001f030c26", "nickname": "momopro箱", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/65da0fc811eaca8c290be7df.jpg", "liked_count": "2", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "5", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061543/a640775812aebfa57bfc5b206a8a35ec/1040g00831g4ibd4chq005p005bi7u31663jlt50!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061543/f2c4e82019677183fd51157cf20dcb40/1040g00831g4ibd4chq0g5p005bi7u3166bn9c30!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,奶昔,抹茶,奶茶测评", "last_modify_ts": 1775461466920, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67f8b528000000001d027ddc?xsec_token=ABXhLyUywH48OxoIW_oDT110_XSqDrye33n-rGsEg81Rg=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABXhLyUywH48OxoIW_oDT110_XSqDrye33n-rGsEg81Rg="}
