{"note_id": "682325e5000000002102c0d2", "type": "normal", "title": "我宣布奈雪的茶在我这是最难喝的奶茶😕", "desc": "点了杯霸气柠檬油柑 一点油柑的涩味和回甘都没有\n像在喝糖水，柠檬糖的味道[失望R]#喝一杯奶茶[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]#\n#喝不腻的果茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1747133925000, "last_update_time": 1747133925000, "user_id": "57c4dcabbd0da52f4e5ea432", "nickname": "黄豆会发芽🌱", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31ckdeijp0u0048lplhean91iap1683g", "liked_count": "6", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "2", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061544/6bb680aff368d256ba0a901c9a8d15af/1040g00831he0jqnkjs0048lplhean91i2gtepgg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "喝一杯奶茶,奶茶测评,喝不腻的果茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461466923, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/682325e5000000002102c0d2?xsec_token=ABpFHHWbEEHC-s3BMg2L-QSXMXiEV-Nc96DBI7VoTdmuw=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABpFHHWbEEHC-s3BMg2L-QSXMXiEV-Nc96DBI7VoTdmuw="}
{"note_id": "67f398af000000001d02ebf5", "type": "normal", "title": "这杯巨巨巨难喝！", "desc": "#喝不了一点[话题]#\n奈雪的这杯超厚芋泥奶茶🧋好难喝啊\n他的芋泥特别难吃是说不出来的那种难吃[哭惹R][哭惹R][哭惹R]\n本来满怀期待的点了这杯的[捂脸R][捂脸R]", "video_url": "", "time": 1744017583000, "last_update_time": 1744017583000, "user_id": "661105d00000000007007ef3", "nickname": "小红薯6611B5E4", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/645b7f257b3e7e60e53504de.jpg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/e5541effb72924f233ea7991549525bf/1040g2sg31fvik801girg5pgh0n81ovnj7t32bdg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "喝不了一点", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672510, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67f398af000000001d02ebf5?xsec_token=ABXdgmmC5xbfEfR0MPWm_Fom82hbLpm_Ud9DWmwcqOcUM=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABXdgmmC5xbfEfR0MPWm_Fom82hbLpm_Ud9DWmwcqOcUM="}
{"note_id": "658690d90000000009021686", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶，香水鸭屎香奶茶巨难喝", "desc": "奈雪怎么变得这么难喝了！！！🥤\n真的越来越水，没啥奶味，茶味也没有，难喝到离谱\n更离谱的是明明那么难喝，跟喝白开水似的，但是却很顶肚子。最离谱的是为了发这个帖子，我还给图片图了哈哈哈哈哈哈、职业病\n\t\n#奈雪の茶[话题]# 真的难喝！！难喝#奈雪鸭屎香水牛乳奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1703317721000, "last_update_time": 1703317721000, "user_id": "56736698b8c8b42ce48552b7", "nickname": "两个瓶", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31evp8pupmo0044diusj9gkln2b4adlg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "5", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/62149add3b568ab55fe043156fe76ac9/1040g2sg30t13dkhok00044diusj9gklnl61f7ao!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪の茶,奈雪鸭屎香水牛乳奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672511, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/658690d90000000009021686?xsec_token=ABCKJgLo3-lcUvmcUOKN0Kt-gq3lDrs1agR76-Ke1zNmU=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABCKJgLo3-lcUvmcUOKN0Kt-gq3lDrs1agR76-Ke1zNmU="}
{"note_id": "695ca381000000000e00d4e6", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪你难喝的要死", "desc": "好难喝好难喝好难喝好难喝好难喝，全是糖精味，为啥这么难喝啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊难喝的我难以下口，最近几次点的几次奈雪都不太好喝，不愿再喝。#奈雪的茶[话题]# #霸气车厘子[话题]##难喝[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1767678849000, "last_update_time": 1767678849000, "user_id": "5f2bbb2e0000000001002f17", "nickname": "喵喵喵", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/646ba9512f398a8a00087ce3.jpg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "2", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/4c7197c82196f93ef953dafbdc601355/note_pre_post_uhdr/1040g3r831r053da6g0705npbncn08boncghus2g!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,霸气车厘子,难喝", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672512, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/695ca381000000000e00d4e6?xsec_token=ABipRYHjEB05izq0zxK0WrXTmlADOCcedgqqdqfBYspPQ=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABipRYHjEB05izq0zxK0WrXTmlADOCcedgqqdqfBYspPQ="}
{"note_id": "66f01b3c0000000025030b51", "type": "normal", "title": "能喝浓茶加浓美式纯抹茶第一次喝奈雪的我", "desc": "之前喝奈雪都是果茶，第一次喝奶茶\n奶茶是下午喝的人是下午嘎的\n头晕恶心想吐心跳加速\n所以是茶底的问题还是这个厚乳的问题\n明天还要上班[黄金薯R]\n想鼠\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1727011644000, "last_update_time": 1727011644000, "user_id": "62941a8a000000001501b59f", "nickname": "momo（戒牛奶版）", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/166ad12ae9a7f6fbb4bbbf88d417895f.jpg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "3", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/25ed89f4600cf072a6d8ddc638b0bf98/1040g00831825i72jk6005okk3a55bdcvja3bh5o!nd_dft_wgth_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/5391b0e314f8959a501f33d7aa217cee/1040g00831825i72jk60g5okk3a55bdcv95os500!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672512, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66f01b3c0000000025030b51?xsec_token=ABZ1eCE7u_If9XY4327cRqmkdG1PDF75grP3aD5nmeQgA=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABZ1eCE7u_If9XY4327cRqmkdG1PDF75grP3aD5nmeQgA="}
