{"note_id": "698431bf000000001a01ec73", "type": "normal", "title": "好难喝啊", "desc": "跟抹茶香水椰简直差太多了\n而且现在的抹茶里面怎么都喜欢加啥米布布啊，喜茶也是\n，目前我觉得抹茶里面香水椰最好喝，有没有其他推荐的\n#奶茶测评[话题]#\n#喝了睡不着[话题]#\n#抹茶[话题]#\n#奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1770271167000, "last_update_time": 1770271168000, "user_id": "59d851b2de5fb454a02879d1", "nickname": "orange", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/601764f33d095c6cfaee4de7.jpg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/66bf1f1a56e2c8b851206a67965b31a5/notes_uhdr/1040g3qg31s6pa4tdls0049sdic8r4uehvogmu98!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶测评,喝了睡不着,抹茶,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672514, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/698431bf000000001a01ec73?xsec_token=AB2T1aCYlCc1ActjqxopyKGYa4t4DLlz_NPez2thyxJkQ=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB2T1aCYlCc1ActjqxopyKGYa4t4DLlz_NPez2thyxJkQ="}
{"note_id": "68e92d580000000007039169", "type": "normal", "title": "避雷避雷！奈家的茶", "desc": "两杯奈雪，大人喝的，都不如给小孩点的这杯！\n[失望R]一杯是咸法酪金色山脉珍珠\n咸法酪的风真是都想蹭一下，but！喝第一口我真是以为拿错了，就是一杯普通不能再普通的珍珠奶茶，我品来品去？满脑子疑问🤔咸法酪体现在哪？没事吧！茶也不突出不香，奶也不淳。\n[失望R]第二杯，浓抹黑珍珠，呵呵呵，这么说吧，要不说有抹茶喝着喝着又是一杯普普的珍珠奶茶！浓在哪里？没有茶百道的浓抹有抹茶味，失望至极！最关键，珍珠也很拉垮，主要是喝了小孩那杯的珍珠，一口就是红糖味糯叽叽的珍珠，对比一下子出来了。\n再见👋拉黑名单#奶茶测评[话题]# #奶茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1760111961000, "last_update_time": 1760111961000, "user_id": "54e82f2a2e1d936419722b92", "nickname": "小新♥北鼻", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/6434329a88c2f4203790562f.jpg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "1", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/cd39aeab653dbd8f7a66593c188caf2a/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831nfcn4r0l070401glenikasiokl4ehg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶测评,奶茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672514, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68e92d580000000007039169?xsec_token=ABYR9ipLXk_LCqHAXjxSic9i3ac2kYkEZEg2EfzXNkKiI=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABYR9ipLXk_LCqHAXjxSic9i3ac2kYkEZEg2EfzXNkKiI="}
{"note_id": "68b93c21000000001d0361ff", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的新品好难喝", "desc": "拿到手不满杯，米布布也很少，两三口就没了，喝了一半感觉很腻口，扔了吧，还是66颗蓝莓桑甚酸奶昔比较好喝#奶茶测评[话题]# #今日奶茶长这样[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1756970017000, "last_update_time": 1756970018000, "user_id": "5ccfdebc0000000017007660", "nickname": "初柚", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/5e78c18f02827f00015c7c5d.jpg", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "25", "share_count": "6", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061546/ce6fd39c962b7e78570df3f5ab5f7e11/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031m0ins1jlm005n6frqu5otj0ehonbng!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奶茶测评,今日奶茶长这样,奈雪的茶", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672515, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68b93c21000000001d0361ff?xsec_token=ABQtlnJKKcqZgmYT6q0xmDB3j64EODihdI7Z_DmbnfNeg=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABQtlnJKKcqZgmYT6q0xmDB3j64EODihdI7Z_DmbnfNeg="}
