{"note_id": "68219cfb000000002002b6ba", "type": "normal", "title": "整个人被这杯奶茶弄得淡淡的……", "desc": "奈雪真有你的，为什么能把牛油果制品做得这么难喝[失望R]\n\t\n口感很稀，根本不觉得是在喝酸奶昔，另外牛油果的香味也不突出，整杯都被毛豆压过一头，像是在喝水加多了的毛豆粥[石化R]如果是为了牛油果和酸奶昔去的，真心建议别点！！\n\t\nps:选的少少甜，倒是真不甜（\n-\n#吃货日常[话题]# #生活记录[话题]# #一起嚯奶茶[话题]# #奶茶测评[话题]# #避雷[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1747033339000, "last_update_time": 1747033340000, "user_id": "5c002e9f000000000500c89f", "nickname": "Mario", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pkvu9dm4k6g4bumakn9vi4v0c7n31o", "liked_count": "1", "collected_count": "1", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061547/e13ec5532011536cf019c3d10db43b93/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831hcged27judg4bumakn9vi4vr1kl7k0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061547/be7c3f8f3634fae2190a9c550fff045d/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831hcged2k3skg4bumakn9vi4vsdai6do!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061547/56a0fef8892d4966120dd16b123c011a/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831hcged2kjojg4bumakn9vi4v8utm8qg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "吃货日常,生活记录,一起嚯奶茶,奶茶测评,避雷", "last_modify_ts": 1775461672518, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/68219cfb000000002002b6ba?xsec_token=AB4XPwxnOHnPXBqZ-K8betaME6-IvYaqMPTLU2xK4oqgU=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB4XPwxnOHnPXBqZ-K8betaME6-IvYaqMPTLU2xK4oqgU="}
