{"note_id": "696f7665000000000a02f75f", "type": "normal", "title": "奈雪的茶这个品也太难喝了吧，就跟刷杯水一样，一点味道也没有，特别难喝，叫什么抹茶，一点抹茶味都没有。喝的我都反胃。\n喝完之后，我去小红书上再搜，原来大家都一致都认为这个很难喝，从去年就开始吐槽，为什么还在？这里这么难喝，能不能给我退款？", "desc": "奈雪的茶这个品也太难喝了吧，就跟刷杯水一样，一点味道也没有，特别难喝，叫什么抹茶，一点抹茶味都没有。喝的我都反胃。\n喝完之后，我去小红书上再搜，原来大家都一致都认为这个很难喝，从去年就开始吐槽，为什么还在？这里这么难喝，能不能给我退款？", "video_url": "", "time": 1768912485000, "last_update_time": 1768912485000, "user_id": "600108fa0000000001008bd2", "nickname": "我要上岸", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31dmlbafkg85g5o0113t092uifc33g1o", "liked_count": "", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061553/8101a4b0f6e76ec8709d7c8b28962e31/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831rihe9a9i8dg5o0113t092uin3q1obg!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1775462079161, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/696f7665000000000a02f75f?xsec_token=ABYPKhwqWD6h3Qm9vL-FC8QRlSTYpImbAFn1_SxrK-7Dc=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABYPKhwqWD6h3Qm9vL-FC8QRlSTYpImbAFn1_SxrK-7Dc="}
{"note_id": "6979ea07000000000e03fd51", "type": "normal", "title": "像喝了一口浓痰", "desc": "奈雪红颜草莓初雪温热的，怎么能这么难喝🫨\n一下午喝下来，还是9成新\n-¥0.01元出 有人要吗\n在扔垃圾桶前决定再给它一次机会，结果一口喝下去，顺着吸管爬上来的那一坨黏腻湿滑的小料，混着液体，再配合着余温，OMG，好新鲜😫\n#奈雪的茶[话题]# #奶茶避雷[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1769597447000, "last_update_time": 1769600627000, "user_id": "5e5b88ec00000000010051a0", "nickname": "火火", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31mjtphkk5i005nirh3m08kd099cee10", "liked_count": "", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "10", "share_count": "3", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061553/a338e9a377b95149d9e3b0e81cf70765/1040g2sg31rsnqtqq2gl05nirh3m08kd0bc1el2o!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "奈雪的茶,奶茶避雷", "last_modify_ts": 1775462079161, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/6979ea07000000000e03fd51?xsec_token=ABrX43w9BDwmxCg0JW59CaT1qJSD8_2AgLhhq2NiPL1LY=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "ABrX43w9BDwmxCg0JW59CaT1qJSD8_2AgLhhq2NiPL1LY="}
{"note_id": "69071bb50000000005003d40", "type": "normal", "title": "踩雷二件套😂", "desc": "挺久没喝奶茶了，想着今天周日来喝一杯，之前不知道在哪个博主说这个好喝，兴致好好来尝试，然后一喝一个不吱声，哈哈哈哈，只能说千人千味，这不是我喜欢的[笑哭R][笑哭R][笑哭R]\n#吃完就后悔[话题]# #奈雪的茶[话题]# #糯香融雪[话题]#", "video_url": "", "time": 1762073525000, "last_update_time": 1762073525000, "user_id": "640087ee000000002a00bfd8", "nickname": "小红薯64019214", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31pj1dm48kk0g5p00gvnahfuoi6p8kuo", "liked_count": "", "collected_count": "", "comment_count": "", "share_count": "1", "ip_location": "", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061553/0e6d3dada1508e71dc6eea8a8b96d364/1040g2sg31ock9oihg6705p00gvnahfuohhkv4e0!nd_dft_wlteh_jpg_3", "tag_list": "吃完就后悔,奈雪的茶,糯香融雪", "last_modify_ts": 1775462079162, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69071bb50000000005003d40?xsec_token=AB8ZrDXGemdU2lMs0_DooNcRzVnGLcWJHajr6BwCjD2nY=&xsec_source=pc_search", "source_keyword": "奈雪奶茶难喝", "xsec_token": "AB8ZrDXGemdU2lMs0_DooNcRzVnGLcWJHajr6BwCjD2nY="}
